(97080, 'ruRU', 'I was Illidari once... left for dead at the Black Temple. Now you will witness the power of my new master!', '', 21154),
(97081, 'ruRU', '', 'We''re not going in there, are we?', 21154),
(97082, 'ruRU', 'So, ''Illidari'', you seek my head, that you might take the Twinblades as your own? Allow me to introduce you to their power... personally.', '', 21154),
(97083, 'ruRU', 'Join me! Unleash your true power. Do not let the weak hold you back!', '', 21154),
