(98689, 'ruRU', 'Watch out!', '', 21154),
(98690, 'ruRU', 'That door is sealed with lightning. We must find a way through!', '', 21154),
(98691, 'ruRU', 'Like I always say, if you can''t reach it, throw something at it. Never fails!', '', 21154),
(98692, 'ruRU', 'Here we are... Magnar''s chamber!', '', 21154),
(98694, 'ruRU', 'Я готов.', 'Я готова.', 21154),
(98695, 'ruRU', 'Knights of the Ebon Blade! Assemble as we honor one of our own!', '', 21154),
(98696, 'ruRU', 'You have all heard the legends of countless battles fought... of trials overcome at great cost.', '', 21154),
(98697, 'ruRU', 'His exemplary deeds in the name of the Ebon Blade have shown him to be one of the best of us, worthy of our highest honor.', '', 21154),
(98699, 'ruRU', 'By the will of the Lich King and upon my authority as Highlord, I declare that $n, wielder of the Blades of the Fallen Prince, will henceforth be known as Deathlord of the Ebon Blade.', '', 21154),
(98700, 'ruRU', 'By the will of the Lich King and upon my authority as Highlord, I declare that $n, wielder of the Maw of the Damned, will henceforth be known as Deathlord of the Ebon Blade.', '', 21154),
(98701, 'ruRU', 'By the will of the Lich King and upon my authority as Highlord, I declare that $n, wielder of Apocalypse, will henceforth be known as Deathlord of the Ebon Blade.', '', 21154),
(98702, 'ruRU', '<При вашем приближении царственный друид внимательно смотрит на вас.>$b$b<Секунду спустя он одобрительно фыркает и величаво склоняет перед вами голову.>', '', 21154),
(98703, 'ruRU', 'You will all bow to him as you once did to me, and carry out his will against the Legion!', '', 21154),
