(98788, 'ruRU', 'Вот бы нам побольше таких героев, как ты, $n...', 'Вот бы нам побольше таких героев, как ты, $n...', 21154),
(98789, 'ruRU', 'Я не помню, что со мной случилось...', 'Я не помню, что со мной случилось...', 21154),
(98790, 'ruRU', 'Спасибо. Мне теперь нужно отлежаться, чтобы прийти в норму.', 'Спасибо. Мне теперь нужно отлежаться, чтобы прийти в норму.', 21154),
(98791, 'ruRU', 'Are you ready to face Magnar with me, $n?', '', 21154),
(98792, 'ruRU', 'Feelin'' fine.', '', 21154),
(98793, 'ruRU', 'I will protect you, Hruthnir.', 'I will protect you, Hruthnir.', 21154),
(98794, 'ruRU', '<Silgryn is shaking uncontrollably and can barely speak.>', '', 21154),
(98795, 'ruRU', 'I am, as you will be. Come, let us go to the Halls of Valor. This mortal warrior will find the revenge you crave...', '', 21154),
(98796, 'ruRU', 'Come with me now, let us dine with Odyn tonight.', '', 21154),
(98797, 'ruRU', 'I... have fallen. Hruthnir... you are a valarjar?', '', 21154),
(98798, 'ruRU', 'I see now. My weapons are yours, warrior. May they bring you glory as you strike down Helya''s minions!', '', 21154),
(98799, 'ruRU', 'Begone from here, trespassers!', '', 21154),
(98800, 'ruRU', 'ENOUGH OF THIS! Guards, punish these outsiders for their insolence!', '', 21154),
(98801, 'ruRU', 'I work all this time to improve the forges and do I get a single word of thanks? No!', '', 21154),
(98802, 'ruRU', 'Make the weapons better, Corvus! Saronite isn''t good enough anymore, Corvus! .. Bah! I''ll show them what I can do to a blade.', '', 21154),
(98803, 'ruRU', 'This tropic air is too damp, makes me feel like there''s flesh hanging from my bones again.', '', 21154),
(98804, 'ruRU', 'It wouldn''t have taken years to rebuild the forges if I had some help!', '', 21154),
(98805, 'ruRU', 'What can Corvus do for you?', '', 21154),
(98806, 'ruRU', '', 'Держать строй, охотники на демонов. За владыку Иллидана!', 21154),
(98807, 'ruRU', 'Не отступать. Никто не должен прорваться!', '', 21154),
(98808, 'ruRU', 'The Dreamgrove is spread thin these days, I fear.$b$bMalorne''s Refuge is a bastion of druidic power in the Broken Isles. We cannot let it fall.', 'The Dreamgrove is spread thin these days, I fear.$b$bMalorne''s Refuge is a bastion of druidic power in the Broken Isles. We cannot let it fall.', 21154),
