(98853, 'ruRU', 'Like Malorne himself, we spend most of our time in the wilds.$b$bIn these dire times, however, seclusion is a luxury no one afford. We must stand together, or we will surely fall.', 'Like Malorne himself, we spend most of our time in the wilds.$b$bIn these dire times, however, seclusion is a luxury no one afford. We must stand together, or we will surely fall.', 21154),
