(102473, 'ruRU', 'Ah, you must be the one I am hearing whispers about. Tales of your great deeds and powerful artifact precede you.$b$bI am Spiritwalker Ebonhorn. I have heard much about you and your journeys beyond these isles.$b$bLet us see if the stories of your heroism are true, shall we?', '', 21154),
