(104293, 'ruRU', 'It would seem that even a pit lord can''t keep you down, warlock.', '', 21154),
(104294, 'ruRU', 'But, what of the rest of the council?', '', 21154),
(104295, 'ruRU', 'One more thing, warlock.', '', 21154),
(104296, 'ruRU', 'With the rest scattered and a dreadlord now on our heels, I think it only appropriate that you take leadership of the council. Through your power, we can rebuild.', '', 21154),
(104297, 'ruRU', 'I name you, $n, the First of the Council of the Black Harvest.', '', 21154),
(104298, 'ruRU', 'May you lead us to glory against the Legion.', '', 21154),
(104299, 'ruRU', 'Come, let us plan the future of the council.', '', 21154),
(104300, 'ruRU', '', '$p, можно тебя на минуту? Срочное сообщение.', 21154),
