(104394, 'ruRU', 'Avast, ye swabs! Raise a mug for the outlaw that''s going to take the Dreadblades from the Dread Admiral Eliza''s cold, dead hands!', '', 21154),
(104395, 'ruRU', 'Hoist the sails! Reel in the anchor! Ready yourselves, ya salty dogs, Azsuna awaits!', '', 21154),
