(104399, 'ruRU', 'Murky waters envelop you, softssskin!', 'Murky waters envelop you, softssskin!', 21154),
(104400, 'ruRU', 'The ssseas rise against you!', 'The ssseas rise against you!', 21154),
(104401, 'ruRU', 'Goldrinn''s power will be ours, $r!', 'Goldrinn''s power will be ours, $r!', 21154),
(104402, 'ruRU', 'The Scythe of Elune belongs to the worgen!', 'The Scythe of Elune belongs to the worgen!', 21154),
(104403, 'ruRU', 'Ssshiver before the Rimescale!', 'Ssshiver before the Rimescale!', 21154),
(104404, 'ruRU', 'Down into the cold depths with you!', 'Down into the cold depths with you!', 21154),
(104405, 'ruRU', 'Мы скормим их василискам!', 'Мы скормим их василискам!', 21154),
(104406, 'ruRU', 'Часть наших родичей они увели в Анклав.', 'Часть наших родичей они увели в Анклав.', 21154),
(104407, 'ruRU', 'Благодарю тебя, $gзащитник:защитница;!', 'Благодарю тебя, $gзащитник:защитница;!', 21154),
(104408, 'ruRU', 'Вот почему я ненавижу пещеры.', 'Вот почему я ненавижу пещеры.', 21154),
(104409, 'ruRU', 'Ночью они застали нас врасплох.', 'Ночью они застали нас врасплох.', 21154),
(104410, 'ruRU', 'Пора свести с ними счеты!', 'Пора свести с ними счеты!', 21154),
(104411, 'ruRU', '', 'Finally free from that cursed mage trap! Such a-', 21154),
(104412, 'ruRU', 'Hey there! I was just enjoying a relaxing vacation on the beach when a chilling sense of dread washed over me. Just what are you up to, I wonder?', '', 21154),
(104413, 'ruRU', '', 'Wait, I recognize that voice...', 21154),
(104414, 'ruRU', 'Oh buttons, what have you done? Hurry, get her back in the cell!', '', 21154),
(104415, 'ruRU', '', 'MILLHOUSE!! You''re next!', 21154),
(104416, 'ruRU', 'Quick, disarm her squirrel bombs before they blow!', '', 21154),
(104417, 'ruRU', 'Now scrap those pesky rocket chickens! They''re going to fire!', '', 21154),
(104418, 'ruRU', 'Now make fun of her hair! It won''t help, but it''ll make her REAAAALLLLY mad!', '', 21154),
(104419, 'ruRU', '', 'Why you... No one insults my hair! NO ONE!', 21154),
(104420, 'ruRU', 'Следуй за мной к площадке!', '', 21154),
(104421, 'ruRU', 'Hoo boy, you really did it!', '', 21154),
(104422, 'ruRU', '', 'I know it was you, Millhouse!', 21154),
(104423, 'ruRU', 'Uh oh.', '', 21154),
(104424, 'ruRU', 'Listen Milly, I can explain!', '', 21154),
(104425, 'ruRU', '', 'Don''t "Milly" me, Millhouse Jerimus Manastorm! I''m coming for you!', 21154),
(104426, 'ruRU', 'That''s not even my middle name!', '', 21154),
(104427, 'ruRU', 'Thanks a lot. You have no idea what you unleashed upon the world today!', '', 21154),
(104428, 'ruRU', 'On a completely unrelated note, I... uh... have to go take care of something...', '', 21154),
(104429, 'ruRU', 'Она готова отвести тебя к предводительнице следопытов Ветрокрылой. Удачи, командир!', '', 21154),
(104430, 'ruRU', 'Защищайте меня! Вы же сказали, что это сработает!', '', 21154),
(104431, 'ruRU', 'The Dark Riders were not always like this. They were once a group of traveling merchants.', '', 21154),
(104432, 'ruRU', 'Unfortunately, they crossed the sorcerer Medivh, and have been cursed to hunt artifacts for him for eternity.', '', 21154),
(104433, 'ruRU', 'Ariden was the first of the Dark Riders, and I believe he leads them now.', '', 21154),
(104434, 'ruRU', 'His camp is still in Deadwind Pass, strangely untouched after all these years.', '', 21154),
(104435, 'ruRU', 'If my convictions are correct, the key to finding the Dark Riders, as well as the artifacts they still covet, can be found there.', '', 21154),
(104436, 'ruRU', 'The worgen led you here as well? This must be where the scythe is being kept!', '', 21154),
(104437, 'ruRU', 'Выдвигаемся! "Край горизонта" уже рядом, за этими холмами.', '', 21154),
(104438, 'ruRU', 'Сражайся с ними. Заслужи свою свободу!', '', 21154),
(104439, 'ruRU', 'А, вот она где. Красотка, правда?', '', 21154),
(104440, 'ruRU', 'Эй! Прочь от моих жевалок!', '', 21154),
(104441, 'ruRU', 'Это мои жевалки! Не трогай их!', '', 21154),
(104442, 'ruRU', 'Ты причиняешь боль моим малышам?!', '', 21154),
(104443, 'ruRU', 'Давайте, парни! Сожрите захватчика.', '', 21154),
(104444, 'ruRU', 'Перестань бить моих малюток!', '', 21154),
(104445, 'ruRU', 'Скрип! Забираем корабль.', '', 21154),
(104446, 'ruRU', 'Проберись мимо охраны и убеди первого помощника в нашей правоте. После этого к тебе присоединимся мы.', '', 21154),
(104447, 'ruRU', '', 'Thank you, $c. I must return to my sisters.', 21154),
(104448, 'ruRU', '', 'Благодарю тебя, $gзащитник:защитница;! А теперь разберемся с подлыми дрогбарами, которые нас поймали.', 21154),
(104449, 'ruRU', '', 'It''s so good to see you again, $n! We really lit Pandaria up together, didn''t we?$b$bI''ve been perfecting my fire spells since you last worked with the Shado-Pan. If you can keep me on my feet, I will be able to break Aspersius''s ice walls and otherwise bring him to a boil. Stand near me and I will enhance the power of your Jade Lightning.$b$b<Fei Li grins savagely.>$b$bDo you want me to REALLY light this thing up or should I concentrate on keeping myself alive?', 21154),
(104450, 'ruRU', '', 'Thank you, $c, for coming to our aid. I am Fei Li, and I have a reputation among the Shado-Pan for setting things on fire. Usually our enemies. Sometimes our Monastery. Lord Taran Zhu isn''t too pleased with me at the moment...$b$bHelp me get back into his good graces. If you can keep me on my feet, I will be able to break Aspersius''s ice walls and otherwise bring him to a boil. Stand near me and my Brilliance Aura will restore your mana.$b$b<Fei Li grins savagely.>$b$bDo you want me to REALLY light this thing up or should I concentrate on keeping myself alive?', 21154),
(104451, 'ruRU', 'We should try to find a way to stop his channeling...', '', 21154),
(104452, 'ruRU', 'Concentrate on staying alive, Fei Li. I need to focus on the others.', 'Concentrate on staying alive, Fei Li. I need to focus on the others.', 21154),
(104453, 'ruRU', 'Do your worst, Fei Li! Even if it puts you in danger. I''ll keep you alive.', 'Do your worst, Fei Li! Even if it puts you in danger. I''ll keep you alive.', 21154),
(104454, 'ruRU', 'Greetings, $n! Your training has progressed far since we last adventured together in Pandaria. I''d venture that even Lord Taran Zhu could learn a thing or two from you. It''s a pleasure to be fighting with you again.$b$bNow, to business! I will assault Aspersius at range while Whitefeather swoops in to harass him with beak and claw. Stand near me and I will help you cast spells faster.$b$bI could go for an all-out attack, but it would put myself at risk. How aggressive should I be?', '', 21154),
(104455, 'ruRU', 'Hello, $c! It is good to have a healer at our side. We are the Shado-Pan, the last defense of Pandaria. I am Hawkmaster Nurong, Master of the Wu Kao discipline - we are the eyes of the Shado-Pan, the scouts who make our enemies fear the darkness.$b$bNow, to business! I will assault Aspersius at range while my hawk Whitefeather swoops in to harass him with beak and claw. Stand near me and I will help you attack faster.$b$bI could go for an all-out attack, but it would put myself at risk. How aggressive should I be?', '', 21154),
(104456, 'ruRU', 'Concentrate on keeping yourself alive, Nurong. Fight defensively.', 'Concentrate on keeping yourself alive, Nurong. Fight defensively.', 21154),
(104457, 'ruRU', 'Do as much damage as you can, Nurong, even if it puts you at risk. I will keep you alive!', 'Do as much damage as you can, Nurong, even if it puts you at risk. I will keep you alive!', 21154),
(104458, 'ruRU', '', '$n! It has been such a long time. You should visit us in Pandaria more often. You and I made a great team.$b$bYou know my strengths, $n. While Taran Zhu holds that thing''s attention, I will stalk it from behind and bury my daggers in any weak spots. I can also help you move quickly around the battlefield - stand near me to reset your roll and flying kick abilities.$b$bHow aggressive do you want me to be? I could throw caution to the wind and wage an all-out assault, but I''ll need to know you have my back�', 21154),
(104459, 'ruRU', '', 'Thank you for your well-timed rescue, $c. We could''ve used your help in the Pandaren Campaign. My name is Taoshi, the silent blade of the Shado-Pan. I slip unseen through enemy territory and strike where they are weakest.$b$bI''ll do my part. While Taran Zhu holds that thing''s attention, I will stalk it from behind and bury my daggers in any weak spots. I can also help you move quickly around the battlefield - stand near me to gain chrarges of your Roll, Chi Torpedo, and Mistwalk abilities.$b$bHow aggressive do you want me to be? I could throw caution to the wind and wage an all-out assault, but I''ll need to know you have my back�', 21154),
(104460, 'ruRU', 'Don''t be too aggressive - keep yourself alive, even if it means sacrificing damage.', 'Don''t be too aggressive - keep yourself alive, even if it means sacrificing damage.', 21154),
(104461, 'ruRU', 'Don''t hold back, Taoshi! Do your worst to that thing and I will keep you alive.', 'Don''t hold back, Taoshi! Do your worst to that thing and I will keep you alive.', 21154),
(104462, 'ruRU', 'С |cFFFF0000|Hspell:199176|h[шипастых языков]|h|r Нараксас начинает стекать слюна!', '', 21154),
(104463, 'ruRU', 'Дрогбары спрыгивают вниз!', 'Дрогбары спрыгивают вниз!', 21154),
(104464, 'ruRU', 'Very well! If you so thirst for the power of the Scythe, then I will show it to you myself!', '', 21154),
(104465, 'ruRU', 'Face the fury of the beast!', '', 21154),
(104466, 'ruRU', 'You have proven an unexpected ally, $c. The Scythe of Elune is yours. Let us hope it can turn the tide in this war.', '', 21154),
(104467, 'ruRU', 'If you want the Scythe, $c, come and claim it!', '', 21154),
(104468, 'ruRU', 'Ох, чую я, это ловушка. Нельзя верить демону на слово!', '', 21154),
(104469, 'ruRU', '', 'Если он лжет, мы казним его. Но что если он говорит правду? Мы должны проверить!', 21154),
(104470, 'ruRU', '', 'Psst! Over here, $n.', 21154),
(104471, 'ruRU', 'Гончая Ужаса взволнованно нюхает воздух.', '', 21154),
(104472, 'ruRU', '$n готовит обильное угощение!', '$n готовит обильное угощение!', 21154),
(104473, 'ruRU', '$n готовит щедрое сурамарское угощение!', '$n готовит щедрое сурамарское угощение!', 21154),
(104474, 'ruRU', 'Вот это предложение, от которого невозможно отказаться! Отступайте к храму! Пусть забирают это корыто!', '', 21154),
(104475, 'ruRU', 'You''ll be findin'' Eliza in the temple ruins ahead. Keep yer wits about ya! Her whole crew''s onto us now.', '', 21154),
(104476, 'ruRU', 'Мы поддержим тебя с моря, как только все наладим.', '', 21154),
(104477, 'ruRU', 'Плохо дело. Я слышу их наверху. Они приближаются. Ладно, я разберусь с ними сам, а ты разделайся с Дьяконом!', '', 21154),
(104478, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\inv_sword_115:20|t %s берет в руки огромный меч и теперь может использовать способность |cFFFF0000|Hspell:199556|h["Жестокая атака"]|h|r!', '', 21154),
