(105518, 'ruRU', 'Это будет славная охота!', 'Это будет славная охота!', 21154),
(105519, 'ruRU', 'You may find it comforting to know that no matter what terrible state you''ve gotten the puzzle into, it is always solvable. This is true in totems as well as life.$b$bStill, sometimes a fresh start can be beneficial.', '', 21154),
(105520, 'ruRU', 'That''s good to know. Can I try again?', 'That''s good to know. Can I try again?', 21154),
