(106803, 'ruRU', 'Теперь налево, и мы почти пришли.', '', 21154),
(106804, 'ruRU', 'Мы на месте! Ты смотри, это же панель управления титанов! Я разберусь, $gприятель:подруга;! А ты проследи, чтобы мне никто не мешал работать.', '', 21154),
(106805, 'ruRU', 'I leave my blade to you. Stromkar deserves to be wielded in battle, not locked away in a tomb. It was forged by a master swordsmith and imbued with elven magics. I know not whether being buried in that beast for centuries has affected it, but I trust that it will serve you well.', '', 21154),
(106806, 'ruRU', '', 'Милуна пытается отдышаться, хлюпая носом.', 21154),
(106807, 'ruRU', '', 'У нас все получится, $n. Г''ханир рассчитывает на нас!', 21154),
(106808, 'ruRU', '', 'The Gilneans think they can take what''s mine. I will have this tower, and their heads. Crush them, for the Horde!', 21154),
(106809, 'ruRU', '', 'Ох, друзья. Я даже не знаю, что и делать!', 21154),
(106810, 'ruRU', '', 'Our forces prevail! Watch them panic and flee as their captain falls before them. For the Horde!', 21154),
(106811, 'ruRU', 'The Forsaken look weak. This tower is ripe for the taking. Show them what happens to enemies of the Alliance!', '', 21154),
(106812, 'ruRU', 'Their lines break, and their captain falls. This is the sound of Gilnean vengeance! For the Alliance!', '', 21154),
