(106933, 'ruRU', 'Use Eviscerate with 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(106934, 'ruRU', '', 'Oh, that Grixis! He''s a cowardly poacher who forces minions to do his dirty work. Show him what we think of his kind.', 21154),
