(108072, 'ruRU', 'This glowing flower very distinctly stands out. It looks to have been meticulously cared for by someone with great horticultural skills.\n\nProbably best to leave this one to someone more in tune with nature.', 'This glowing flower very distinctly stands out. It looks to have been meticulously cared for by someone with great horticultural skills.\n\nProbably best to leave this one to someone more in tune with nature.', 21154),
