(108076, 'ruRU', 'To think I would live to see such profane use of runic magic. It saddens my heart.', '', 21154),
(108077, 'ruRU', 'There''s nothing here.', 'There''s nothing here.', 21154),
(108078, 'ruRU', '', 'We shall meet again, $n. May Elune guide our paths.', 21154),
(108079, 'ruRU', 'Сорвав здесь цветок, вы выпустите бодрящие споры. Вы знаете это, потому что изучали травничество и разбираетесь в растениях.', 'Сорвав здесь цветок, вы выпустите бодрящие споры. Вы знаете это, потому что изучали травничество и разбираетесь в растениях.', 21154),
(108080, 'ruRU', 'Breathe deep of its spores. As a Druid, you are attuned to nature and can recognize this flower''s beneficial properties.', 'Breathe deep of its spores. As a Druid, you are attuned to nature and can recognize this flower''s beneficial properties.', 21154),
(108081, 'ruRU', 'We are everywhere. We are Legion.', '', 21154),
(108082, 'ruRU', 'Meddling... whelp...', '', 21154),
(108083, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a subtlety rogue you specialize in striking from the shadows, dispatching foes quickly and quietly. Let''s begin your training with your primary attack, Backstab.', '', 21154),
(108084, 'ruRU', 'Use Backstab on this target dummy. Attacking from behind inflicts more damage.', '', 21154),
(108085, 'ruRU', '', 'Demons continue to march on the Gates of the Valor. Your aid is required.', 21154),
(108086, 'ruRU', '', 'You have done well this day, champion. May the Twisting Nether be filled with the lamentations of your enemies.', 21154),
(108087, 'ruRU', 'What brings you to this lawless place?', '', 21154),
(108088, 'ruRU', 'The shadows reveal.', 'The shadows reveal.', 21154),
(108089, 'ruRU', 'The Burning Legion. Slayers of whole worlds.', '', 21154),
(108090, 'ruRU', 'Could we hope to resist? Can you?!', '', 21154),
(108091, 'ruRU', 'Held to the majesty of the stars, you are nothing - less than nothing.', '', 21154),
(108092, 'ruRU', 'What are you exactly?', 'What are you exactly?', 21154),
(108093, 'ruRU', 'What meager petulance. I expected more from you.', '', 21154),
(108094, 'ruRU', 'Is that not enough? Must I show you the true horror of our reality?', '', 21154),
(108095, 'ruRU', 'Very well... witness what I have seen, and TREMBLE!', '', 21154),
(108096, 'ruRU', 'Avatars of non-existence... knowing nothing but hunger.', '', 21154),
(108097, 'ruRU', 'These are the beings who will devour the future you so futilely fight to protect!', '', 21154),
(108098, 'ruRU', 'No... I cannot control... the void... it comes!', '', 21154),
(108099, 'ruRU', 'I provide information that no other can.$B$BThat is all you need to know.', '', 21154),
(108100, 'ruRU', 'The stars have judged you, and found you wanting.', '', 21154),
(108101, 'ruRU', 'Let''s get back to the matter at hand.', 'Let''s get back to the matter at hand.', 21154),
(108102, 'ruRU', '', 'Those creatures over there are empowered by ancient mana. It is awful to ask this of you, but I need you to dispatch them and siphon their energy.', 21154),
(108103, 'ruRU', 'It seems fate is on your side, rogue.', '', 21154),
(108104, 'ruRU', '', 'Thank you. It is a horrid duty, but this work is essential for our survival.', 21154),
(108105, 'ruRU', 'Akaari is in this very city as we speak - spying for her masters.', '', 21154),
(108106, 'ruRU', 'I will gladly tell you where... in exchange for a rune of portals.', '', 21154),
(108107, 'ruRU', 'Until then our business is complete.', '', 21154),
(108108, 'ruRU', '', 'We go to the Temple of Elune. We will ride more swiftly on Ash''alah''s back. Are you ready to depart?', 21154),
(108109, 'ruRU', '', 'We go to the Temple of Elune. Ash''alah will carry you this once. Prepare yourself.', 21154),
(108110, 'ruRU', 'Greetings! Are you here to see my exquisite collection?', '', 21154),
(108111, 'ruRU', 'If you are here to see my most prized possession, I am afraid that I have it locked away.$b$bI might bring it out in a hundred years or so. Would you like to make an appointment?', '', 21154),
