(108556, 'ruRU', 'A priest, thank the Light!', '', 21154),
(108557, 'ruRU', '', 'Give yourself over, as I did.', 21154),
(108558, 'ruRU', '', 'At last... the long dream comes.', 21154),
(108559, 'ruRU', 'Begone mortals! The time of the Windlords has passed!', '', 21154),
(108560, 'ruRU', 'Foolish shaman! You really think that Thunderaan can save your world?', '', 21154),
(108561, 'ruRU', 'I will devour you and take the Staff of Four Winds for myself!', '', 21154),
(108562, 'ruRU', '', 'The Nightmare is inescapable.', 21154),
(108563, 'ruRU', 'Listen well, Farseer... I will aid the Earthen Ring for now.', '', 21154),
(108564, 'ruRU', 'The armies of Skywall shall stand shoulder to shoulder with the mortal races in battle against the Burning Legion.', '', 21154),
(108565, 'ruRU', 'When the fog of battle clears, and the Burning Legion is defeated, we shall stand victorious!', '', 21154),
(108566, 'ruRU', '', 'Spirits of the forest, guardians of nature, hear our call!', 21154),
(108567, 'ruRU', '', 'On this day, the mother tree is reborn - G''Hanir is whole once more!', 21154),
(108568, 'ruRU', 'Come on, $p, talk with Sternfathom. Let''s get this fight started!', '', 21154),
(108569, 'ruRU', 'AAAAHHHHHHHHhhhh...!', '', 21154),
(108570, 'ruRU', 'Let''s give them a moment to regroup and prepare, $n.\n\nWhen they''re ready, speak with me again, and I''ll throw you into the arena to get this fight started.', '', 21154),
(108571, 'ruRU', 'What''re you lookin'' at? Ain''t ye ever seen a sea lion before?', '', 21154),
(108572, 'ruRU', 'Not like this...', 'Not like this...', 21154),
(108573, 'ruRU', 'Yes, I''m a druid and... well... I''m kind of stuck like this for a while.$b$bWhile patrolling the sea around the Broken Shore, an infernal crashed into the water right on top of me. The blast instantly knocked me unconscious.\n$b$bWhen I woke I was here in the care of the nurses. They say after a few days I should have the strength to shift back. In the meantime, I''m stuck in this contraption to keep me from drying out.\n$b$bDo me a favor. Don''t mention this to any of the other druids. They''ll never let me live it down!', '', 21154),
(108574, 'ruRU', 'Come, we shall use the garden entrance.', '', 21154),
(108575, 'ruRU', 'Enchanted masks. Simply don the mask, and a magical costume will envelop your body.', '', 21154),
(108576, 'ruRU', 'I will find Ly''leth. You stay out of trouble.', '', 21154),
(108577, 'ruRU', 'It should be enough to fool the other guests, but stay clear of the guards.', '', 21154),
(108578, 'ruRU', 'The fangs are within your grasp!', '', 21154),
(108579, 'ruRU', 'Use the signal lantern to alert Ly''leth Lunastre of your arrival.', 'Use the signal lantern to alert Ly''leth Lunastre of your arrival.', 21154),
(108580, 'ruRU', 'This lantern appears to have been slightly modified. It must be the one you need to use to send a signal.', 'This lantern appears to have been slightly modified. It must be the one you need to use to send a signal.', 21154),
(108581, 'ruRU', 'Send a signal to Ly''leth Lunastre.', 'Send a signal to Ly''leth Lunastre.', 21154),
(108582, 'ruRU', '', 'Ah, it is good to see you again. Tonight, the nobles are throwing a party in the honor of the Grand Magistrix.', 21154),
(108583, 'ruRU', '', 'Our spies report that Elisande herself will be in attendance. This will be one of the few opportunities we have to catch her away from her source of power.', 21154),
(108584, 'ruRU', '', 'We''ll have to take a side entrance to the grounds... the front is being too heavily watched.', 21154),
(108585, 'ruRU', '', 'Fantastic job so far. I can provide you a basic disguise to get in... It will trick the nobles, but it might not fool anyone with a keen eye.', 21154),
(108586, 'ruRU', '', 'This is your best shot at eliminating the Grand Magistrix. Good luck in there!', 21154),
(108587, 'ruRU', '', 'Kill them, you fools! I will not be denied my destiny!', 21154),
(108588, 'ruRU', 'I... I need fresh air!', '', 21154),
(108589, 'ruRU', 'Among the souls you have rescued, there are some who wish to regain their honor fighting alongside you against the kvaldir.', '', 21154),
(108590, 'ruRU', 'We must not suffer Helya''s minions to gain territory unfought. Your loyalty shall be rewarded.', '', 21154),
(108591, 'ruRU', 'It''s over, Zithreen! Tell us... what did Azshara plan to do with this realm?', '', 21154),
(108592, 'ruRU', '', 'I will tell you NOTHING!', 21154),
(108593, 'ruRU', 'Agraaahh!!', '', 21154),
(108594, 'ruRU', 'Well then... I guess... I guess we''re done talking here.', '', 21154),
(108595, 'ruRU', 'Dead now.', '', 21154),
(108596, 'ruRU', 'A Legion vessel! Galiaan - make haste for Stormwind! Danuvin - secure the grounds! We will hold them off as long as we can. The rest of you - get to your positions!', '', 21154),
(108597, 'ruRU', 'Barrem!', '', 21154),
(108598, 'ruRU', 'I greet you, $n. I am glad to help.', '', 21154),
(108599, 'ruRU', 'Orik says you can speak to these spirits, how do we begin?', 'Orik says you can speak to these spirits, how do we begin?', 21154),
(108600, 'ruRU', 'I misjudged how long ago this happened. I will need more time to prepare myself for the ritual.$b$bIn the meantime, I have attuned this stone to the scroll Orik brought. Certain graves will glow to your mind''s eye. Go to them and concentrate on the stone to see if you have found the correct grave. We want the writer himself, not a descendent or ancestor.', '', 21154),
(108601, 'ruRU', 'The stone grows dull, this is the wrong grave. A relative probably.', 'The stone grows dull, this is the wrong grave. A relative probably.', 21154),
(108602, 'ruRU', 'Concentrating', 'Concentrating', 21154),
(108603, 'ruRU', 'The stone glows brightly, this is the correct grave!', 'The stone glows brightly, this is the correct grave!', 21154),
(108604, 'ruRU', '', 'Yes, what is it? I am very busy planning my next gala.', 21154),
(108605, 'ruRU', '', 'Oh, you again! I cannot thank you enough for what you did, dear.$b$bI am already hearing good things about the new jeweler. Perhaps I should pay him a visit and get a new piece commissioned...', 21154),
(108606, 'ruRU', 'I wanted to speak with you about a gem design.', 'I wanted to speak with you about a gem design.', 21154),
(108607, 'ruRU', 'Champion, a great malevolence has risen in the mists. Gather your most powerful allies and meet the kvaldir in battle!', '', 21154),
(108608, 'ruRU', 'Even my most loyal vrykul dare not enter the mists for fear of their souls. I commend your bravery, mortal.', '', 21154),
(108609, 'ruRU', 'There''s a portal to Wyrmrest Temple in that new tower in the middle of Dalaran, that should get you most of the way there. Tahu, thanks again fer doing this, for helping us paladins.', '', 21154),
(108610, 'ruRU', 'I hope I can bring success to your quest, Orik. You asked the Sunwalkers for aid and I have come.', '', 21154),
(108611, 'ruRU', 'You made it! This land haunts me still, so much pain and death here. Let''s get on with it.', '', 21154),
(108612, 'ruRU', 'Find them. Akaari will not be disturbed!', '', 21154),
(108613, 'ruRU', 'Light give me strength!', '', 21154),
(108614, 'ruRU', 'For the Alliance!', '', 21154),
(108615, 'ruRU', 'Begone foul beast!', '', 21154),
(108616, 'ruRU', '', 'Ты нуждаешься в исцелении?', 21154),
(108617, 'ruRU', 'Я ищу шалдорайский шелк. У вас его не найдется?', 'Я ищу шалдорайский шелк. У вас его не найдется?', 21154),
(108618, 'ruRU', '', 'О да, конечно, вон в том сундуке. Только не бери слишком много, а то нам самим не хватит.', 21154),
(108619, 'ruRU', 'А есть в этих местах хороший портной?', 'А есть в этих местах хороший портной?', 21154),
(108620, 'ruRU', '', 'Не так давно тут проходила ткачиха силовых линий из Сурамара. Вроде бы она направлялась на восток к Лесному водопаду.', 21154),
(108621, 'ruRU', 'My beasts have been blessed by the Light to enhance their speed and agility. You''ll not find a swifter ride.', '', 21154),
(108622, 'ruRU', 'I''d like to travel to Dalaran.', 'I''d like to travel to Dalaran.', 21154),
(108623, 'ruRU', '', 'Find somewhere safe! I''ll find you when this is over.', 21154),
(108624, 'ruRU', 'Those tendrils are using dark magic to become immune to attack. Interrupt their casting so you can strike!', '', 21154),
(108625, 'ruRU', 'I don''t have time for idle chatter, $n.', '', 21154),
(108626, 'ruRU', 'To arms!', 'To arms!', 21154),
(108627, 'ruRU', 'Если не сложно, ты не могла бы заштопать это для меня?', 'Если не сложно, ты не могла бы заштопать это для меня?', 21154),
(108629, 'ruRU', 'What do you want, warlock? Can''t you see I''m busy?', '', 21154),
(108630, 'ruRU', 'Who summoned all these imps?', 'Who summoned all these imps?', 21154),
(108631, 'ruRU', '', 'И ты смеешь обращаться ко мне с таким ничтожным поручением? Ты шутишь, наверное?$b$bЧто, нет? Ясно. Что ж, я не первый день за пределами Сурамара и способна распознать алхимика.$b$bЯ выполню твою просьбу, если ты выполнишь мою.$b$bИзготовь для меня зелье Сна Изеры. Это древнее эльфийское зелье, для приготовления которого нужен грезолист и Слезы Спящего.$b$bЭти растения можно собрать неподалеку отсюда, среди руин. Воз', 21154),
(108632, 'ruRU', '', 'Ты меня не интересуешь. Я принадлежу к знаменитой династии портных Сурамара. А ты, очевидно, нет.', 21154),
(108633, 'ruRU', 'Confess your crimes!', 'Confess your crimes!', 21154),
(108634, 'ruRU', '', 'Приветствую, ткач силовых линий. Могу я чем-то тебе помочь?', 21154),
(108635, 'ruRU', '', 'Какая удача! Коллега-$gпортной:портниха;!$b$bДобро пожаловать в гильдию ткачей силовых линий Сурамара. Быть может, тебе доводилось о нас слышать?', 21154),
(108636, 'ruRU', '', 'Ты $gпринес:принесла; мне зелье?', 21154),
(108637, 'ruRU', 'Вот твое зелье.', 'Вот твое зелье.', 21154),
(108638, 'ruRU', 'Crimes? The only thing I am guilty of is being the most powerful warlock in all of Azeroth!', '', 21154),
(108639, 'ruRU', '', 'Да, этого достаточно. Ну, показывай мне свой шелк.', 21154),
(108640, 'ruRU', 'Lespin wants his brooch back.', 'Lespin wants his brooch back.', 21154),
(108641, 'ruRU', 'Come minions, aid me in battle against this accuser!', '', 21154),
(108642, 'ruRU', 'Minions...?', '', 21154),
(108643, 'ruRU', '', 'Вот, держи. И ступай отсюда.', 21154),
(108644, 'ruRU', 'Progress is slow, but steady. I will be back in the good graces of the courts soon, and it is all thanks to you.', '', 21154),
(108645, 'ruRU', 'He''s just inside. Please, do whatever you can to save him.', '', 21154),
(108646, 'ruRU', 'What do you want? I have few friends in these dark days. I am prepared to defend myself!', '', 21154),
(108647, 'ruRU', 'The Fel Magic reacts violently to your spell!', 'The Fel Magic reacts violently to your spell!', 21154),
(108648, 'ruRU', 'We have found you, and you have found the grave.', '', 21154),
(108649, 'ruRU', 'What is the next step?', '', 21154),
(108650, 'ruRU', 'I will begin the ritual. You must focus your will upon the spirit while our friend keeps us safe.', '', 21154),
(108651, 'ruRU', 'Let''s get to it then.', '', 21154),
(108652, 'ruRU', 'I died to ease the pain of my failure, why do you disturb me?!', '', 21154),
(108653, 'ruRU', 'I read your saga, where did you find the shield?', '', 21154),
(108654, 'ruRU', 'I must answer. I followed it across many lands and seas until I reached an island in Stormheim. There was a tomb for the kings there. For months I tried to enter the shrine, but I was not a follower of Tyr''s path and was denied. I returned in disgrace and tried to cleanse my failure in the blood of others.', '', 21154),
(108655, 'ruRU', 'We will finish what you started.', '', 21154),
(108656, 'ruRU', 'Return to your rest and be disgraced no more.', '', 21154),
(108657, 'ruRU', 'I''m coming with you, $n. You helped one of my men so it''s only fitting that I return the favor for you.', '', 21154),
(108658, 'ruRU', 'I''ll meet you at Krasus'' Landing, we can take my gryphon down to the island.', '', 21154),
(108659, 'ruRU', 'Thank you Tahu for your help. I will remember this.', '', 21154),
(108660, 'ruRU', 'I am glad to have helped. I must go to Netherlight Temple and inform the Cardinal of our success. Good luck.', '', 21154),
(108661, 'ruRU', 'As for you, let''s get back to Dalaran quick. I''ll meet you there.', '', 21154),
(108662, 'ruRU', 'Stop, please! I''ll pen a confession, assuming you didn''t break my writing hand...', '', 21154),
(108663, 'ruRU', '', 'I foresaw your coming, of course. The threads of fate that led you to this place. Your desperate attempt to stop the Legion.', 21154),
(108664, 'ruRU', '', 'My people faced a similar dilemma. I peered into all possible futures in search of an answer... and found only one.', 21154),
(108665, 'ruRU', '', 'The Legion''s victory is inevitable. Every time stream shows it to be so. Had we resisted, they would have taken the Nightwell by force and left us bereft of it.', 21154),
(108666, 'ruRU', '', 'I could not allow my people to starve, to waste away without its energies sustaining us. So a bargain was struck.', 21154),
(108667, 'ruRU', '', 'Now I see a future where the Legion is victorious and my people endure. This is the thread that must be preserved. I will do everything in my power to make it so!', 21154),
(108668, 'ruRU', '', 'Your deaths ensure the future of the Nightborne. Come forward, then. Let us speed you toward your fate.', 21154),
(108669, 'ruRU', '', 'Your timelines end here!', 21154),
(108670, 'ruRU', '', 'The threads of time answer to me!', 21154),
(108671, 'ruRU', '', 'Will you race through time? Or be trapped in an endless eternity?', 21154),
(108672, 'ruRU', '', 'Time itself heeds my call!', 21154),
(108673, 'ruRU', '', 'I control the battlefield, not you!', 21154),
(108674, 'ruRU', '', 'Let the waves of time crash over you!', 21154),
(108675, 'ruRU', '', 'You''ll find time can be quite volatile.', 21154),
(108676, 'ruRU', '', 'You exist in but a single moment. I am far less limited!', 21154),
(108677, 'ruRU', '', 'Time shifts again, and your doom draws near!', 21154),
(108678, 'ruRU', '', 'The time streams are mine to command! You cannot win!', 21154),
(108679, 'ruRU', '', 'Time is... slipping away! How can it be so?', 21154),
(108680, 'ruRU', '', 'Just as I foretold.', 21154),
(108681, 'ruRU', '', 'An inevitable outcome.', 21154),
(108682, 'ruRU', '', 'You were destined to die.', 21154),
(108683, 'ruRU', '', 'It''s... not possible! I... I was destined to win...', 21154),
(108684, 'ruRU', '', 'I take no joy in this victory, but it was inevitable.', 21154),
(108685, 'ruRU', '', 'In all the possible futures I scryed, I did not foresee one in which you were victorious. I wonder...', 21154),
(108686, 'ruRU', '', 'Will you defeat the Legion? Will you fail? Time eddies about you in fits and starts. Nothing is certain!', 21154),
(108687, 'ruRU', '', 'Perhaps you will win. And in saving your world, my people would be freed from the terrible bargain we were forced to make.', 21154),
(108688, 'ruRU', '', 'Fates be damned! I cast my lot in with yours, champions. Go now, face Gul''dan. I will aid you as best I can, and perhaps together we can save us all.', 21154),
(108689, 'ruRU', 'I can see your future mortal.', '', 21154),
(108690, 'ruRU', 'Want to know the exact time and date of your death?', '', 21154),
(108691, 'ruRU', 'Just as I foresaw it.', '', 21154),
(108692, 'ruRU', 'My sight diminishes.', '', 21154),
(108693, 'ruRU', 'Sacrifices must be made.', '', 21154),
(108694, 'ruRU', 'All will turn to ash.', '', 21154),
(108695, 'ruRU', 'I already know your next move.', '', 21154),
(108696, 'ruRU', 'All answer to their fate.', '', 21154),
(108697, 'ruRU', 'Your fate betrays you mortal', '', 21154),
(108698, 'ruRU', 'Hello? Is anyone out there? I can''t see...', '', 21154),
(108699, 'ruRU', 'Uh... not me. Definitely not me.\n\nLike I told the guards in Dalaran, it''s probably the Fizzlebang girl. Just like her brother, always summoning a mess of demons she can''t control.', '', 21154),
(108700, 'ruRU', 'Be quick! I wouldn''t want us to be caught off guard while you''re browsing my wares.', '', 21154),
(108701, 'ruRU', 'Lulubelle says you''re to blame.', 'Lulubelle says you''re to blame.', 21154),
(108702, 'ruRU', 'She would say that, wouldn''t she? Further proof that you can''t trust a Fizzlebang!', '', 21154),
(108703, 'ruRU', '', 'Welcome, Lord of Flame. Welcome, Kil''jaeden!', 21154),
(108704, 'ruRU', 'You have done well, Akaari. You have earned my blessing.', '', 21154),
(108705, 'ruRU', 'Azhir manari kirel. Akim manari galar!', '', 21154),
(108706, 'ruRU', '', 'The fangs... their power is beyond comprehension! I am your humble servant, my lord!', 21154),
(108707, 'ruRU', 'It is time for your true test. Use the Fangs of the Devourer and slay your uninvited guest.', '', 21154),
(108708, 'ruRU', 'Thanks to you I have already begun to rebuild my friendships. I tell all of them that you saved me from a nefarious plot to exile me.', '', 21154),
(108709, 'ruRU', 'My brooch? Bah, I have bigger things to worry about than Lespin. Unfortunately for you, I no longer have the brooch.$b$bIt was stolen by Venlis Swiftsea, undoubtedly part of some plot to assassinate my reputation. It is a clever move, since now I cannot be seen near him.$b$bIf you were to go "speak" with him and recover the brooch, I think we would both benefit from this mess.', '', 21154),
(108711, 'ruRU', '', 'The Legion has always been one step ahead of us, but I believe we can turn the tables. There is a seer using its demonic eyes to foresee events. We must disrupt it.', 21154),
(108712, 'ruRU', '', 'The demon''s foresight is confounded, at least for a time. This gives us a window to move on our other operations.', 21154),
(108713, 'ruRU', '', 'The design he wants? It belonged to my husband, not him. That wretch Lespin murdered my dear husband. $b$bI had him entombed in a small cave north of the city, for we could not afford the trip to Tel''anor. Buried with him is the tome he kept all his designs in.$b$bRetrieve the design and keep it out of his hands!', 21154),
(108714, 'ruRU', '', 'Who knows when this will end?', 21154),
(108715, 'ruRU', 'Has it passed? I can''t wait to warm up baked goods for our troops once this is all over.', '', 21154),
(108716, 'ruRU', '', 'They will taste blood in your name!', 21154),
(108717, 'ruRU', '', 'The specters here continue to concoct a wine so foul it serves only to poison the drinker. Azsuna would be better served with them gone.', 21154),
(108718, 'ruRU', '', 'That should help to contain the spread of their corrupted... spirits. You have my thanks.', 21154),
(108719, 'ruRU', '$n! You can''t just sneak up on someone like that. Not while this is going on! $B$BIf you need me to fix something better make it quick. I''m on watch.', '', 21154),
(108720, 'ruRU', '', 'Imps aren''t ideal test subjects. They''re easy enough to summon, but often too fragile for my experiments.', 21154),
(108721, 'ruRU', 'Feel its power coursing through you, shaman. The waters that Azshara tried to turn against us are now yours to command.', '', 21154),
(108722, 'ruRU', 'Magic stick!', '', 21154),
(108723, 'ruRU', 'Come, let us return to the others.', '', 21154),
(108724, 'ruRU', '', 'I never thought I would someday long for the peace and quiet of the Maelstrom.', 21154),
(108725, 'ruRU', 'Ularogg enters the |cFFFF0000|Hspell:198510|h[Stance of the Mountain]|h|r!', '', 21154),
(108726, 'ruRU', 'It''s a book. That floats. Why did the demons leave it here?', 'It''s a book. That floats. Why did the demons leave it here?', 21154),
(108727, 'ruRU', 'It''s a book. That floats. Why did the demons leave it here?\n\nIt looks sinister, but probably not worth your time.', 'It''s a book. That floats. Why did the demons leave it here?\n\nIt looks sinister, but probably not worth your time.', 21154),
(108728, 'ruRU', 'Dedication to your holy Paladin order demands that you purify this fel taint.', 'Dedication to your holy Paladin order demands that you purify this fel taint.', 21154),
(108729, 'ruRU', 'This book is unnatural to Priests and must be destroyed.', 'This book is unnatural to Priests and must be destroyed.', 21154),
(108730, 'ruRU', 'Let''s fly, $n. Lightfeather is saddled and ready to go.', '', 21154),
(108731, 'ruRU', 'The demons of Faronaar seek to bend the Illidari to their will. This must not be allowed to transpire!', '', 21154),
(108732, 'ruRU', 'With the Illidari freed, the demons'' threat is contained. You have done a great service to our land, champion.', '', 21154),
(108733, 'ruRU', '', 'These demons are even more persistent than the wretched naga! We must drive them back! My Nightwatchers will aid you.', 21154),
(108734, 'ruRU', '', 'Ha! That should teach them not to tangle with the Nightwatchers!', 21154),
(108735, 'ruRU', 'It pains me to see my brethren reduced to such a state. There is nothing left for them now but hunger. Please, put them to rest.', '', 21154),
(108736, 'ruRU', 'It was a dark task, but one that needed to be done. You have my gratitude, champion.', '', 21154),
(108737, 'ruRU', '', 'First the naga assault our city! Now it looks like they''re trying to make off with our relics as well. Show them what it means to incur the wrath of the Nightwatchers, champion!', 21154),
(108738, 'ruRU', '', 'That should teach the naga to stay out of Azsuna! The citizens of Nar''thalas owe you a debt of gratitude, $c, as do the Nightwatchers.', 21154),
(108739, 'ruRU', 'Bad enough that naga and demons invade our home... now these makrura plague our shores! We must find out what dark force is driving them to madness. Will you help?', '', 21154),
(108740, 'ruRU', 'So the foul demons were behind it all! You have my thanks for foiling their scheme. Without the demons inciting them, the makrura threat should subside.', '', 21154),
(108741, 'ruRU', '', 'The audacity of these scaly cretins is truly limitless! Now they dare disgrace the city of Nar''thalas with their presence? As a friend of the Nightwatchers, you must not let this stand!', 21154),
(108742, 'ruRU', '', 'I commend your bravery, champion. The Nightwatchers will take care of their remaining forces. We are in your debt.', 21154),
(108743, 'ruRU', 'If the sea giants wish to ally with the naga, then they have become our enemy. Champion, show them that the Highborne are not to be trifled with!', '', 21154),
(108744, 'ruRU', 'Let that be a lesson they will not soon forget. Thank you, champion.', '', 21154),
(108745, 'ruRU', 'I just soiled myself...', '', 21154),
(108748, 'ruRU', 'Rokmora rears back for |cFFFF0000|Hspell:188169|h[Razor Shards]|h|r!', '', 21154),
(108749, 'ruRU', 'Fish-breath still alive.$b$bYou ready for fighting?', '', 21154),
(108750, 'ruRU', 'Let''s do it!', 'Let''s do it!', 21154),
(108751, 'ruRU', 'Snake witch powerful, but with Grash help kill!', '', 21154),
(108752, 'ruRU', 'Let''s finish this, Grash!', 'Let''s finish this, Grash!', 21154),
(108753, 'ruRU', 'They''ve taken the fields!', '', 21154),
(108754, 'ruRU', 'Protect the Hill at all costs!', '', 21154),
(108755, 'ruRU', 'Everything I''ve worked for... gone!', '', 21154),
(108756, 'ruRU', 'All of our crops were destroyed!', '', 21154),
(108757, 'ruRU', 'Ain''t never been formally trained, but I''m sure this here pointy end means trouble.', '', 21154),
(108758, 'ruRU', 'There! In the skies! More of our reinforcements! Hold strong!', '', 21154),
(108759, 'ruRU', '', 'Let us finish this once and for all.', 21154),
(108760, 'ruRU', '', 'Do you feel the fangs'' bite withering the flesh off your very bones?', 21154),
(108761, 'ruRU', '', 'Mephistroth guide my hand - I will not fail!', 21154),
(108762, 'ruRU', '', 'I have broken entire worlds from the inside out. Azeroth will crumble!', 21154),
(108763, 'ruRU', '', 'No more games.', 21154),
(108764, 'ruRU', '', 'Join me... in the nether...', 21154),
(108765, 'ruRU', 'The citadel has begun a self-destruction sequence. Make your way to the portal once you have the fangs!', '', 21154),
(108766, 'ruRU', '', 'Can you feel your mind slipping away?', 21154),
(108767, 'ruRU', '', 'I am your end!', 21154),
(108768, 'ruRU', 'This creature is using its own life essence to harm us! He is dying with every attack!', '', 21154),
(108769, 'ruRU', 'Clever. Now he''s channeling his own flame back into his body to become whole again.', '', 21154),
(108770, 'ruRU', 'Hero, we must figure out a way to stop him from replenishing his life source! Perhaps you could use your magic to make him change his mind... You know, trick him into snuffing out his own flame!', '', 21154),
(108771, 'ruRU', 'Ah, you made it. Well done!', '', 21154),
(108772, 'ruRU', 'Valeera said you would know where to meet her upon your return. Not one I would desire to keep waiting.', '', 21154),
(108773, 'ruRU', 'Until our paths cross again.', '', 21154),
(108774, 'ruRU', 'Come with me. The depths await!', '', 21154),
(108775, 'ruRU', 'That Beast is already trying to take her soul! Hurry, we might still be able to save her!', '', 21154),
(108776, 'ruRU', 'Jump on Azuregos''s back to avoid |cFFFF0404|Hspell:209863|h[Force of Gravity]|h|r!', 'Jump on Azuregos''s back to avoid |cFFFF0404|Hspell:209863|h[Force of Gravity]|h|r!', 21154),
(108777, 'ruRU', 'Mage reinforcements are arriving from Stormwind! Put aside your hostilities! We fight together as one!', '', 21154),
(108778, 'ruRU', 'Light protect us! Here they come!', '', 21154),
(108779, 'ruRU', 'Sir.', '', 21154),
(108780, 'ruRU', 'For the Alliance!', 'For the Alliance!', 21154),
(108781, 'ruRU', 'Hold the gates!', 'Hold the gates!', 21154),
(108782, 'ruRU', 'Reporting for duty!', 'Reporting for duty!', 21154),
(108783, 'ruRU', 'Point me to the nearest demon!', 'Point me to the nearest demon!', 21154),
(108784, 'ruRU', 'Mum.', 'Mum.', 21154),
(108785, 'ruRU', '', 'I''m sorry, but what does, "Mum" mean? Is there something you need?', 21154),
(108786, 'ruRU', 'Oh, uh... well I''m looking for some burettes?', 'Oh, uh... well I''m looking for some burettes?', 21154),
(108787, 'ruRU', '', 'Well why didn''t you just say so to begin with? There aren''t any guards around, we''re perfectly safe to speak freely.', 21154),
(108788, 'ruRU', 'How in the light am I supposed to get a hair from an archmage?!', 'How in the light am I supposed to get a hair from an archmage?!', 21154),
(108789, 'ruRU', '', 'Judging by what you''re asking for I assume you''re an alchemist?$b$bAnd if that''s true, isn''t there some sort of invisibility potion you can brew? Skaggldrynk I believe it''s called.$b$bHe''ll never see you coming.', 21154),
(108790, 'ruRU', 'Carefully pluck a single strand of hair from Khadgar''s head.', 'Carefully pluck a single strand of hair from Khadgar''s head.', 21154),
(108791, 'ruRU', 'OW!! What in the light was that?!', '', 21154),
(108792, 'ruRU', 'Something... bit my head I think.', '', 21154),
(108793, 'ruRU', 'If you can pay, I can supply.', '', 21154),
(108794, 'ruRU', 'Show me what you have available.', 'Show me what you have available.', 21154),
(108795, 'ruRU', '', 'Khadgar, what''s wrong? What happened?', 21154),
(108796, 'ruRU', '<Lay your insignia on the table.>', '<Lay your insignia on the table.>', 21154),
(108797, 'ruRU', '', 'Something bit your head? That''s all? Would you like me to kiss it for you?', 21154),
(108798, 'ruRU', 'Just mount the bird here and follow me! To Stormheim!', '', 21154),
(108799, 'ruRU', 'Your order''s in the back room, $Gsir:madame;.', '', 21154),
(108800, 'ruRU', 'Right this way, $GMister:Miss; $n.', '', 21154),
(108801, 'ruRU', 'Hm, |5$r of your tastes might find our private selection in the back to your liking.', '', 21154),
(108802, 'ruRU', 'Welcome back, $Gsir:madame;. Might I suggest you check out our new arrivals in the VIP room?', '', 21154),
(108803, 'ruRU', 'Use |TInterface\\Icons\\spell_warlock_demonicportal_green.blp:20|t |cFFFF0000|Hspell:111771|h[Demonic Gateway]|h|r to get past Ariden''s barrier!', 'Use |TInterface\\Icons\\spell_warlock_demonicportal_green.blp:20|t |cFFFF0000|Hspell:111771|h[Demonic Portal]|h|r to get past Ariden''s barrier!', 21154),
(108804, 'ruRU', 'The Darkbrul Arena is a place for the clans to challenge each other. Get in there and prove that the Stonedark and their allies are the toughest!', '', 21154),
(108805, 'ruRU', 'Please, keep your voice down!$b$bIf they catch me talking to you... they''ll kill me!', 'Please, keep your voice down!$b$bIf they catch me talking to you... they''ll kill me!', 21154),
(108806, 'ruRU', 'I''ve cleared a path for you. You can escape if you hurry!', 'I''ve cleared a path for you. You can escape if you hurry!', 21154),
(108807, 'ruRU', '', 'Impossible! To think some hairy air-breather with legs has won the day... It''s disgusting! Begone, champion!', 21154),
(108808, 'ruRU', '', 'That was a legendary performance! Thank you for proving that friendship is overrated.', 21154),
(108809, 'ruRU', 'The raven calls.', 'The raven calls.', 21154),
(108810, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\ability_fomor_boss_shout:20|t%s begins a |cFFFF0404|Hspell:209748|h[Deafening Roar]|h|r. Stop casting!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\ability_fomor_boss_shout:20|t%s begins a |cFFFF0404|Hspell:209748|h[Deafening Roar]|h|r. Stop casting!', 21154),
(108811, 'ruRU', 'And we will answer from the shadows.', '', 21154),
(108812, 'ruRU', 'I never thought I would make it out alive!', 'I never thought I would make it out alive!', 21154),
(108813, 'ruRU', 'The Twilight''s Hammer must be stopped!', 'The Twilight''s Hammer must be stopped!', 21154),
(108814, 'ruRU', 'I never thought I''d see my children''s faces again!', 'I never thought I''d see my children''s faces again!', 21154),
(108815, 'ruRU', 'I can''t wait to take a bath!', 'I can''t wait to take a bath!', 21154),
(108816, 'ruRU', 'Please save the others, hero!', 'Please save the others, hero!', 21154),
(108817, 'ruRU', 'Be careful. I''ve seen The Master... and she''s powerful!', 'Be careful. I''ve seen The Master... and she''s powerful!', 21154),
(108818, 'ruRU', 'We''re saved!', 'We''re saved!', 21154),
(108819, 'ruRU', 'You fight with a fury worthy of a vrykul! An infant or elderly vrykul, but a vrykul all the same! Well done!', '', 21154),
(108820, 'ruRU', 'You''ve saved me. I won''t forget this!', 'You''ve saved me. I won''t forget this!', 21154),
(108821, 'ruRU', '', 'Through the ages, the mightiest naga have come to this strand to test their mettle against their kin. Prove your worth and we may let you leave here alive, outsider!', 21154),
(108822, 'ruRU', '', 'Welcome to the Black Rook Rumble! Did you come here to fight alongside friends or allies? Well, send them away! Within this arena, you stand alone.', 21154),
(108823, 'ruRU', 'Looking for something specific today?', '', 21154),
(108824, 'ruRU', '', 'That odd wyrmtongue over there seems to be gesturing towards you. Be on guard, this could be a trick!', 21154),
(108825, 'ruRU', '', 'That reprehensible little worm has learned its lesson. Well fought!', 21154),
(108826, 'ruRU', '$p, I didn''t realize it was you - my apologies. The Uncrowned await your arrival.', '', 21154),
(108827, 'ruRU', 'This a placeholder event for imbuing the Moonwell. Spell effects will be added at a later date.', '', 21154),
(108828, 'ruRU', 'That there be $p. I heard $Ghe:she; took down Deathwing with nothin'' but the blades in $Ghis:her; hands!', 'Looking for something specific today?', 21154),
(108829, 'ruRU', 'We would like you to do the honors, friend. Come.', '', 21154),
(108831, 'ruRU', 'Ey mon, dat there be da one Garona spoke of.', '', 21154),
(108832, 'ruRU', '', 'Yes, thank you for all you have done.', 21154),
(108833, 'ruRU', 'Mayruna kneels and arranges a silver basin on the ground, then pours a small amount of glowing water into it.', 'Mayruna kneels and arranges a silver basin on the ground, then pours a small amount of softly glowing liquid into it.', 21154),
(108834, 'ruRU', '', 'Whenever you are ready, simply submerge the ritual bundle.', 21154),
(108837, 'ruRU', '', 'Mother Moon, goddess of my heart, bless this place with your light.', 21154),
(108838, 'ruRU', 'On behalf of the Sablehorn, let this moonwell be blessed.', '', 21154),
(108839, 'ruRU', 'On behalf of the Feathermane, let this moonwell be blessed.', '', 21154),
(108840, 'ruRU', '', 'On behalf of the Moonwhisper, let this moonwell be blessed.', 21154),
(108841, 'ruRU', '', 'Mm. It is done. Thank you again for making this possible.', 21154),
(108842, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\spell_shaman_lavaflow.blp:20|t %s readies |cFFF00000|Hspell:200404|h[Magma Wave]|h|r. Hide!', '', 21154),
(108843, 'ruRU', '', 'I will not... give in!', 21154),
(108844, 'ruRU', 'Your torment only feeds the nightmare, weakling!', '', 21154),
(108845, 'ruRU', '', 'The power of the Caduceus is MINE to command!', 21154),
(108846, 'ruRU', 'I''m telling you Cato, the shield is here! I can feel it!', '', 21154),
(108847, 'ruRU', '', 'You will drown in this place!', 21154),
(108848, 'ruRU', '', 'The Earthen Ring will never have Azshara''s power!', 21154),
(108849, 'ruRU', 'I''m here aren''t I? Let''s find your shield and get back to the war.', '', 21154),
(108850, 'ruRU', 'Here''s my friend now. Glad you could make it. There''s the tomb, let''s get in there and find that shrine! We''ll follow your lead.', '', 21154),
(108851, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Spell_Nature_LightningOverload:20|t You are afflicted with |cFFFF0000|Hspell:204275|h[Arcane Tether]|h|r!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Spell_Nature_LightningOverload:20|t You are afflicted with |cFFFF0000|Hspell:204275|h[Arcane Tether]|h|r!', 21154),
(108852, 'ruRU', '', 'I owe you a great debt, druid. I will not forget this.', 21154),
(108853, 'ruRU', 'Ummm...?', 'Ummm...?', 21154),
(108854, 'ruRU', 'Look, this one is not my fault. How was I supposed to know those demons would believe me?', '', 21154),
(108855, 'ruRU', 'To the Sentinel Hill! Let us put an end to this!', '', 21154),
(108856, 'ruRU', 'Petty mortals. Your world will end soon enough!', '', 21154),
(108857, 'ruRU', 'Take cover! More infernals incoming!', '', 21154),
(108858, 'ruRU', 'Watch the skies, I sense them coming.', '', 21154),
(108859, 'ruRU', 'Don''t waste your breath, druid. Malorne''s gift is ours. Now, join your ancestors!', '', 21154),
(108860, 'ruRU', '', 'The Bloodstone is ready. Handle it with care, $n.', 21154),
(108861, 'ruRU', 'Nooooooooo!', '', 21154),
(108862, 'ruRU', 'Cannot. Control. Must. KILL!', '', 21154),
(108863, 'ruRU', 'Grash no let puny shaman hurt snake lady!', '', 21154),
(108864, 'ruRU', 'Thank you again for giving me the honor of sacrificing my life for the cause. Now you know that I''d willingly give everything to further Lord Illidan''s plan. The Burning Legion must be destroyed at any cost.\n\nI owe you everything, $n.\n\nNow, you complete what we started, gain the Sargerite Keystone, and return triumphant to the Black Temple.\n\nLord Illidan awaits.', '', 21154),
(108866, 'ruRU', '', 'When the summoning is complete, channel the stone''s power to gain control over the twin demons.', 21154),
(108867, 'ruRU', 'Well I didn''t think they would actually believe me.', '', 21154),
(108868, 'ruRU', 'You demon toying fool! You have compromised our position.', '', 21154),
(108869, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Affliction warlocks use shadow magic and disease to wear down their enemies, then drain their very life essences to empower themselves. Your command of dark magic enables you to summon a demon servant to do your bidding.', '', 21154),
(108870, 'ruRU', 'Use Summon Voidwalker to summon your demonic minion.', '', 21154),
(108871, 'ruRU', 'Agony is an appropriate name for your first attack ability. Agony deals more and more damage over time, making it a great way to start a fight.', '', 21154),
(108872, 'ruRU', 'Use Agony on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(108873, 'ruRU', 'Warlocks inflict suffering on anyone foolish enough to fight them. Corruption is a spell that afflicts its target, dealing shadow damage as long as the affliction lasts.', '', 21154),
(108874, 'ruRU', 'Use Corruption on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(108875, 'ruRU', 'After afflicting your target with Agony and Corruption, you can begin to drain the very life from them. Drain Life is the most frequent attack you will use, healing you as it damages your foe.', '', 21154),
(108876, 'ruRU', 'Use Drain Life on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(108877, 'ruRU', 'As Agony damages your enemy, it has a chance to generate a Soul Shard. You can use these shards to empower new abilities. Unstable Affliction is a powerful spell that deals damage over time like Agony and Corruption, but uses a Soul Shard to deal more damage.', '', 21154),
(108878, 'ruRU', 'Use Unstable Affliction on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(108879, 'ruRU', 'Now that you have all your primary attack abilities, we will see how they work together!', '', 21154),
(108880, 'ruRU', 'Practice using your attacks on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(108881, 'ruRU', 'Many spells have a heavy mana cost. Warlocks have a clever way around this problem. Life Tap allows you to steal your own life force to replenish your mana. Don''t worry, you can always drain the life from your opponent to heal.', '', 21154),
(108882, 'ruRU', 'Use Life Tap to replenish your mana reserves.', '', 21154),
(108883, 'ruRU', 'At times you may find yourself overwhelmed by multiple enemies, or a single enemy that is too strong for you. To force a foe to stop fighting for a short time, utilize fear itself to strike terror into their heart.', '', 21154),
(108884, 'ruRU', 'Use Fear to frighten this soldier.', '', 21154),
(108885, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as an affliction warlock.', '', 21154),
(108886, 'ruRU', 'Council members and allies, it is time to begin the summoning.', '', 21154),
(108887, 'ruRU', 'We employ a variety of methods to ensure Azeroth remains safe, and to ensure our rightful place within it.', '', 21154),
(108888, 'ruRU', 'But the events at the Broken Shore have forced our hand. We haven''t the time for subtlety.', '', 21154),
(108889, 'ruRU', 'T... T''uure... Alora... escape...', '', 21154),
(108890, 'ruRU', 'You know the deal. We kill $Ghim:her;, our debts are clear!', 'You know the deal. We kill $Ghim:her;, our debts are clear!', 21154),
(108891, 'ruRU', 'Nothing personal, friend. Just business.', 'Nothing personal, friend. Just business.', 21154),
(108892, 'ruRU', 'Consider your choice carefully.', '', 21154),
(108893, 'ruRU', 'The Uncrowned will do what no others can: finish this war.', '', 21154),
(108894, 'ruRU', 'I''m ready to make a decision.', 'I''m ready to make a decision.', 21154),
(108895, 'ruRU', '', 'What''s the matter - never seen a princess that knows how to twist a blade?', 21154),
(108896, 'ruRU', 'Tell me about your plan.', 'Tell me about your plan.', 21154),
(108897, 'ruRU', '', 'Garona hid the Kingslayers for good reason; their power is not to be underestimated.$B$BI need your help to retrieve them. They may be the only blades that can destroy Gul''dan and his foul allies.', 21154),
(108898, 'ruRU', 'Give me your ear, $n. I''ve got a plan that''s guaranteed to put worthy blades in yer hands!', '', 21154),
(108899, 'ruRU', 'What can I do for ya?', '', 21154),
(108900, 'ruRU', '', 'The Kingslayers are the only way to ensure the Legion''s end. Hear me out, won''t you?', 21154),
(108901, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ve nearly located the eredar we''ve been hunting for years. With some help we can take her out and lay claim to her daggers.', 21154),
(108902, 'ruRU', 'Shortly after the Cataclysm one of me best discovered a pair of golden cutlasses, unlike any you''ve ever seen. They say the moment Eliza touched ''em she had a vision of herself at the head of her own fleet, conquering city after city with a crew of lost souls.$B$BI don''t know if ye believe in grand tales like that, but it indeed came to pass. The Dreadblades have claimed countless souls, but what the Dread Admiral doesn''t know is that we''re comin'' for ''em!', '', 21154),
(108903, 'ruRU', '', 'Jorach spoke highly of you. He''s a good friend to have.', 21154),
(108904, 'ruRU', '', 'After the fall of Sargeras'' personal hound Goremaw, his dreadlords took the hound''s best fangs and forged them into a pair of daggers known as the Fangs of the Devourer. They say they still carry their master''s bite.$B$BSargeras called upon one of his top assassins to wield the fangs - Akaari Shadowgore. We''ve been after her ever since, and despite our attempts we haven''t been able to stop her.', 21154),
(108905, 'ruRU', 'You won''t escape from me this time, Valith! Tell me where your master is and I just might finish you off quickly.', '', 21154),
(108906, 'ruRU', 'Well done, champions! Let us regroup and - By the Light... Sentinel Tower! Quickly!', '', 21154),
(108907, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Spell_DeathKnight_MindFreeze:20|t%s casts |cFFFF0404|Hspell:209983|h[Control Thoughts]|h|r on Grash!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Spell_DeathKnight_MindFreeze:20|t%s casts |cFFFF0404|Hspell:209983|h[Control Thoughts]|h|r on Grash!', 21154),
(108908, 'ruRU', 'That insignia marks you as one of us. Carry it with you always.', '', 21154),
(108909, 'ruRU', 'My work will shine for eternity...', '', 21154),
(108910, 'ruRU', 'A Rotdrool Grabber bursts from the husk of the grub!', '', 21154),
(108911, 'ruRU', 'Go deal with that demon, $n! I''ll tend to Alora.', '', 21154),
(108912, 'ruRU', 'I seem to have misplaced my insignia.', 'I seem to have misplaced my insignia.', 21154),
(108913, 'ruRU', 'Knocking', 'Knocking', 21154),
(108914, 'ruRU', '', 'Use your feral form to heighten your senses, $n. Between the three of us, we can pick up the satyr''s trail.', 21154),
(108915, 'ruRU', 'The barrier you placed here with Ysondre''s Tear still stands.\n\nIf you wish, you can remove it.', 'The barrier you placed here with Ysondre''s Tear still stands.\n\nIf you wish, you can remove it.', 21154),
(108916, 'ruRU', 'Remove the seal.', 'Remove the seal.', 21154),
(108917, 'ruRU', '', 'Foolish warlocks, summoning what you cannot control.', 21154),
(108918, 'ruRU', 'The doomguards make their descent! Prepare yourselves!', '', 21154),
(108919, 'ruRU', '', 'You will meet your death by our hands!', 21154),
(108920, 'ruRU', 'Sinu a''manore, You were lucky that I was in the area. What brings you to this forsaken place?', '', 21154),
(108921, 'ruRU', 'Look there! I don''t think that tablet was glowing when I first saw it. Odd, I can read it.', '', 21154),
(108922, 'ruRU', 'I had thought my battle over. You have my gratitude.', 'I had thought my battle over. You have my gratitude.', 21154),
(108923, 'ruRU', 'Thank you. I shall return to the Illidari to recover.', 'Thank you. I shall return to the Illidari to recover.', 21154),
(108924, 'ruRU', 'These foul demons sap our strength and seek to bend our will. Show them no mercy!', 'These foul demons sap our strength and seek to bend our will. Show them no mercy!', 21154),
(108925, 'ruRU', 'When that brute Kraggosh and his overseers moved into the Undercity, we were forced to do our real work in secret.$B$BSurely you can see how such an arrangement inevitably led me here.', '', 21154),
(108926, 'ruRU', 'It shames me to have been taken alive by these creatures. Thanks to you, I will fight another day.', 'It shames me to have been taken alive by these creatures. Thanks to you, I will fight another day.', 21154),
(108927, 'ruRU', 'Thank you for freeing me, $c. The Illidari must learn what the Legion is planning in Faronaar!', 'Thank you for freeing me, $c. The Illidari must learn what the Legion is planning in Faronaar!', 21154),
(108928, 'ruRU', 'Out here, no one will hear your screams!', '', 21154),
(108929, 'ruRU', 'Your god is no match for ours, druid!', '', 21154),
(108931, 'ruRU', 'Oh, that reminds me. While you were off doing the easy work, I was out taking care of the other part that was needed.', '', 21154),
(108932, 'ruRU', 'Just... resting my eyes... for a moment...', '', 21154),
(108933, 'ruRU', 'Come, we have much to discuss.', '', 21154),
(108934, 'ruRU', 'I had to deal with those awful scribes over at The Scribe''s Sacellum. But, ultimately, it was worth the effort.', '', 21154),
(108935, 'ruRU', 'That should do it. I think we both deserve a pat on the back, $n. Wouldn''t you agree?', '', 21154),
(108936, 'ruRU', 'Give up, druid. Your ancient god... cannot... be saved...', '', 21154),
(108937, 'ruRU', 'It''s no use, druid. You cannot fight us.', '', 21154),
(108938, 'ruRU', 'Only in the Nightmare do you see absolute truth, untarnished by hope.', '', 21154),
(108939, 'ruRU', 'Against us, your strength is nothing. All you love will turn against you. You will face your greatest fears.', '', 21154),
(108940, 'ruRU', '', 'Who goes there?', 21154),
(108941, 'ruRU', 'Thank you for that welcome distraction.', '', 21154),
(108942, 'ruRU', 'Sylendra, is there any way we can still recover the idol?', '', 21154),
(108943, 'ruRU', 'Just enjoy the party for a bit. You know... mingle.', '', 21154),
(108944, 'ruRU', 'Let us gather and give our oaths!', '', 21154),
(108945, 'ruRU', '<The attendant is silent.>', '<The attendant is silent.>', 21154),
(108946, 'ruRU', '<Take a drink.>', '<Take a drink.>', 21154),
(108947, 'ruRU', '', 'There are more people trapped in there. Please, rescue them too if you can. Thank you again, $n!', 21154),
(108948, 'ruRU', 'I choose you to be the Sixth.', 'I choose you to be the Sixth.', 21154),
(108949, 'ruRU', '', 'I can see the times are changing.  \n\nOne warlock, no matter how powerful, can''t take on the Burning Legion alone.\n\nWhile I''ll never believe anything Ritssyn does is selfless, it''s clear that rebuilding the council is the right thing to do.\n\nI would be honored to count myself one among the six, if you''ll have me.', 21154),
(108950, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ll do whatever it takes to restore pride to the Fizzlebang name.', 21154),
(108951, 'ruRU', '', 'It takes many years to build a reputation, and only one mistake to tarnish it.\n\nI have my work cut out for me, but I hope that serving on the council will help towards restoring pride to the Fizzlebang name.', 21154),
(108952, 'ruRU', 'Let''s get going, the portal is just ahead.', '', 21154),
(108953, 'ruRU', 'The spirits, the elements, they are but pitiful shadows compared to the power of the legion.', '', 21154),
(108954, 'ruRU', 'Bow, bow to the might of Sargeras. Bow and receive his gifts.', '', 21154),
(108955, 'ruRU', 'The forces of Highmountain, the drogbar, even the elves, will be swept away in the flames of our wrath.', '', 21154),
(108956, 'ruRU', 'Embrace the fel energies of our new masters. Kneel, and you shall rise stronger than ever.', '', 21154),
(108957, 'ruRU', '', 'Too many of the Bloodtotem have gone over to the legion. Now, these Feltotem are gathering their strength. I do not intend to let their betrayal go unpunished.', 21154),
(108958, 'ruRU', '', 'The Bloodtotem had been growing more distant for years now. But to side with the Legion? None of us could have foreseen that.', 21154),
(108959, 'ruRU', 'By our blades! For the Alliance!', '', 21154),
(108960, 'ruRU', 'Fools! Our forces have spread across these foul lands. We have defiled and corrupted your precious soil... Let us see how you deal with our legion now.', '', 21154),
(108961, 'ruRU', 'Members of the Alliance! Spread out and put an end to this corruption!', '', 21154),
(108962, 'ruRU', 'Don''t bother reading it or anything.', '', 21154),
(108963, 'ruRU', 'Just go ahead and sign it.', '', 21154),
(108964, 'ruRU', 'Right there on the line.', '', 21154),
(108965, 'ruRU', 'This metal is all bent out of shape. A strong Blacksmith could hammer these pieces back into working order.', 'This metal is all bent out of shape. A strong Blacksmith could hammer these pieces back into working order.', 21154),
(108966, 'ruRU', 'The Idol is ours! Take it back to the Dreamgrove. Sylendra and I will meet you there.', '', 21154),
(108967, 'ruRU', 'Someone left some goods out in the open...', 'Someone left some goods out in the open...', 21154),
(108968, 'ruRU', 'It would be a pity if a Warrior were to smash them.', 'It would be a pity if a Warrior were to smash them.', 21154),
(108969, 'ruRU', 'If a Rogue were to pilfer some of these, you''re sure someone would take notice.', 'If a Rogue were to pilfer some of these, you''re sure someone would take notice.', 21154),
(108970, 'ruRU', 'Someone left some goods out in the open...\n\nThey seem to be monitored by magical means.', 'Someone left some goods out in the open...\n\nThey seem to be monitored by magical means.', 21154),
(108971, 'ruRU', 'Halt!', '', 21154),
(108972, 'ruRU', '', 'Betrayers! Liars! Murderers! Has Hamuul sent his lapdogs to fetch the knife from my back?', 21154),
(108973, 'ruRU', 'Guards! To me!', '', 21154),
(108974, 'ruRU', '', 'Do you remember murdering me? Or have you grown so used to slaughter that my cries of agony are long forgotten?', 21154),
(108975, 'ruRU', '', 'I recall my final moments surrounded by those I had trusted. Your satisfied sneers as I drew my last breath.', 21154),
(108976, 'ruRU', '', 'Revenge is said to be sweet, but I taste only bitterness.', 21154),
(108977, 'ruRU', '', 'Your faces no longer appear familiar. Did you truly deserve my wrath?', 21154),
(108978, 'ruRU', '', 'Now you have become prey!', 21154),
(108979, 'ruRU', '', 'Scurry, scurry, little rats!', 21154),
(108980, 'ruRU', '', 'There is nowhere left to hide!', 21154),
(108981, 'ruRU', '', 'Such juicy morsels!', 21154),
(108982, 'ruRU', '', 'Scream for me as I drain you!', 21154),
(108983, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ll adorn my web with your bones!', 21154),
(108984, 'ruRU', '', 'Feel the crush of my talons!', 21154),
(108985, 'ruRU', '', 'My beak will tear your flesh, vermin!', 21154),
(108986, 'ruRU', '', 'Not afraid of spiders, are you?', 21154),
(108987, 'ruRU', 'You took your time getting here. I''ll make this quick.', '', 21154),
(108988, 'ruRU', '', 'This time I''m ready for your treachery!', 21154),
