(109031, 'ruRU', 'This tablet tells a grand tale. It appears trying to open these doors will hit you with some kind of power. My guess is you might be strong and pure-hearted enough to give it a shot.', '', 21154),
(109032, 'ruRU', 'This magical lantern is different in some way. Almost as if it is leaking.', 'This magical lantern is different in some way. Almost as if it is leaking.', 21154),
(109033, 'ruRU', 'As a Mage, you are long familiar with the intricacies of ley magic. It can be repurposed to a... better cause.', 'As a Mage, you are long familiar with the intricacies of ley magic. It can be repurposed to a... better cause.', 21154),
(109034, 'ruRU', 'This faulty device of Elven construct is familiar to you and can be altered to provide magical empowerment.', 'This faulty device of Elven construct is familiar to you and can be altered to provide magical empowerment.', 21154),
(109035, 'ruRU', 'This magical lantern is different in some way. Almost as if it is leaking.\n\nYou''re sure someone will come along and fix it in due time.', 'This magical lantern is different in some way. Almost as if it is leaking.\n\nYou''re sure someone will come along and fix it in due time.', 21154),
(109036, 'ruRU', 'The cultists are blinded by the twilight... deprived and recluse, taking cover in the night.', '', 21154),
(109037, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Beast master hunters possess a deep bond with their pets, calling and bolstering them in battle while striking at foes with ranged attacks. Alongside your trusty pet, you are the master of your environment. Summon Pet will call your pet to your side.', '', 21154),
(109038, 'ruRU', 'Use Call Pet to bring your pet to battle.', '', 21154),
(109039, 'ruRU', 'Sending your pet to attack and distract an enemy gives you more time to line up your ranged attacks. Don''t worry, your pet is resilient! Using Kill Command will cause your pet to perform a strong attack, and is also a great way to initiate a fight.', '', 21154),
(109040, 'ruRU', 'Use Kill Command multiple times on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109041, 'ruRU', 'Now let''s see what other forces of nature you command. Dire Beast will allow you to summon a nearby beast to join the fight and attack your target for a short time.', '', 21154),
(109042, 'ruRU', 'Use Dire Beast on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109043, 'ruRU', 'I''m sure you''re ready to join in on the action. Cobra Shot is your primary ranged attack, pummeling your enemy while your pet keeps their attention.', '', 21154),
(109044, 'ruRU', 'Use Cobra Shot on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109045, 'ruRU', 'Use Bestial Wrath while attacking the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109046, 'ruRU', 'When in combat, Bestial Wrath sends you and your pet into a frenzy of rage that increases your damage for a short time.  While under its effects, using Dire Beast will shorten the time before you can trigger Bestial Wrath again.', '', 21154),
(109049, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you''ll find yourself outnumbered. A skilled hunter can unleash destruction upon a host of adversaries at once! Multi-shot allows you to fire a spread of projectiles hitting several enemies near your target. Using this attack causes your pet to cleave multiple enemies as well.', '', 21154),
(109050, 'ruRU', 'Use Multishot to dispatch all the enemies.', '', 21154),
(109051, 'ruRU', 'Even the greatest hunters sometimes find themselves in over their heads. When facing certain defeat, use Feign Death to trick your enemies into thinking you''re no longer a threat.', '', 21154),
(109052, 'ruRU', 'Use Feign Death to trick my soldier into stopping his attack.', '', 21154),
(109053, 'ruRU', 'Prove to me you have all the skill and cunning of a hunter!', '', 21154),
(109054, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the courage and zeal of a paladin!', '', 21154),
(109056, 'ruRU', 'Target practice is over, $p. It''s time to prove your mettle. Combine all the lessons you''ve learned and use them to defeat my men in combat.', '', 21154),
(109057, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a beast master hunter.', '', 21154),
(109058, 'ruRU', 'Golarb is unresponsive.', '', 21154),
(109059, 'ruRU', 'Mistress is gone...', '', 21154),
