(109086, 'ruRU', 'So be it. Come my wounded friends, let us see if I might have the strength that is needed to carry you to safety.', '', 21154),
(109087, 'ruRU', '', 'This is not up for debate, Anarys. You are either with us, or against us. Choose wisely.', 21154),
