(109090, 'ruRU', 'Thank you, champion. Now that my strength is renewed I should be able to remove this foul magic.', '', 21154),
(109091, 'ruRU', 'Come hero, Jace was headed this way when we were separated.', '', 21154),
(109092, 'ruRU', 'I have waited a long time for someone like you. I sense you are the blood and have the heart. Face me in battle and we will test your strength.', '', 21154),
