(109105, 'ruRU', 'I am not leaving, child. And that is that. No underking is going to scare me out of MY home.', '', 21154),
(109106, 'ruRU', 'I name you, $n, the First of the Council of the Black Harvest.', '', 21154),
(109107, 'ruRU', 'Fah! This is OUR mountain. Let the drogbar savages come. We have the power of the spirits, of this mountain. All they have are sticks and stones and anger.', '', 21154),
(109108, 'ruRU', 'Alright $n, you may want to stand back. Things are going to get hot.', '', 21154),
(109109, 'ruRU', 'Adding the sulfate now.', '', 21154),
(109110, 'ruRU', 'And last but not least, the dust.', '', 21154),
(109111, 'ruRU', 'Success! I have to say, this is some of my finest work. I guess some credit goes to Deucus and his detailed design.', '', 21154),
(109112, 'ruRU', 'Jace went to scout ahead, but when these demons attacked and put up this barrier we became separated. He should still be out there.', '', 21154),
