(109153, 'ruRU', 'You will suffer horrors...', '', 21154),
(109154, 'ruRU', 'Thank you, friends. I admit, I''m surprised you were able to survive the demons trap, Boros. I thought it would be just me and $n now.', '', 21154),
(109155, 'ruRU', 'They closed the gates to the upper levels. $n, destroy the Anchoring Crystal with your holy magic, that should deprive the gates of their power.', '', 21154),
(109156, 'ruRU', '', 'Howww did it get passst the  daughters?! We will feassst on its insssides!', 21154),
(109157, 'ruRU', 'Thank you. Now get out of here! It''s not safe!', 'Thank you. Now get out of here! It''s not safe!', 21154),
(109158, 'ruRU', 'Brave of you to come, but we need to leave!', 'Brave of you to come, but we need to leave!', 21154),
(109159, 'ruRU', 'Never thought I''d see the day...', 'Never thought I''d see the day...', 21154),
