(109164, 'ruRU', 'Easy, Huey! Easy!', '', 21154),
(109165, 'ruRU', '', 'Perhaps she possesses the key to unlocking their knowledge.', 21154),
(109166, 'ruRU', '', 'Garuhod may have been onto something, but I think he got his ingredients mixed up. We should try a different combination. Maybe hydra eggs and murloc eyes?', 21154),
(109167, 'ruRU', '', 'Yes, these should do nicely. Now I just need to find someone to test this on...', 21154),
(109168, 'ruRU', '', 'Enjoying the party?', 21154),
(109169, 'ruRU', '', 'Ah, you must be the outlander Silgryn has told me about.', 21154),
(109170, 'ruRU', 'Pleased to meet you, Lady Ly''leth.', 'Pleased to meet you, Lady Ly''leth.', 21154),
(109171, 'ruRU', 'Sup.', 'Sup.', 21154),
(109172, 'ruRU', '', 'Well, aren''t you charming?', 21154),
(109173, 'ruRU', 'Excellent! Now let''s get out of here.', '', 21154),
(109174, 'ruRU', 'Be on your guard, I sense a powerful demon ahead.', '', 21154),
(109175, 'ruRU', 'Nonsense. What good are my works on the necks of those abominations? You would do well to learn from our friend here.', '', 21154),
(109176, 'ruRU', 'Hop on and let''s get movin''. Ol'' Huey don''t bite... much!', '', 21154),
(109177, 'ruRU', 'Master, this is desecration! They were once our brothers and sisters...', '', 21154),
(109178, 'ruRU', 'If you had faith in the light, Demon Hunter, there would be nothing to fear!', '', 21154),
(109179, 'ruRU', 'It does not matter what could happen to his reputation. He has already ruined it. This is why you are still an apprentice.', '', 21154),
(109180, 'ruRU', 'But master, this man was innocent! His name was cleared, surely he deserves a second chance?', '', 21154),
(109181, 'ruRU', 'You have done everyone a great service, friend. Give cousin Ly''leth my regards. A good merchant knows how to keep his friends and contacts, just in case they have need of each other.', '', 21154),
(109182, 'ruRU', 'To Shield''s Rest!', '', 21154),
