(109899, 'ruRU', 'BLERG!', '', 21154),
(109900, 'ruRU', 'Blerg?', '', 21154),
(109901, 'ruRU', 'Your allies have fallen! %s retreats!', 'Your allies have fallen! %s retreats!', 21154),
(109902, 'ruRU', 'Shaman, you braved the tempest with a peaceful mind. Your focus inspires me. Go now, with my blessings upon you.', '', 21154),
(109903, 'ruRU', 'At last we can begin. Now we will need to move quickly once the ritual is complete, it will close this tomb permanently once the hammer is in our possession.', '', 21154),
(109904, 'ruRU', 'Something is wrong. One of the globes isn''t working! Blast!', '', 21154),
(109905, 'ruRU', 'It must have been taken, perhaps by one of the crazed monsters. It can only be below and we need it. Whenever you are ready, champion.', '', 21154),
(109906, 'ruRU', 'Somehow they must have knocked it loose and taken it below. We must venture further into the depths and find it or this has all been for naught.', '', 21154),
(109907, 'ruRU', 'Our whelplings hunger for the flesh of the moose, but the young ones cannot stomach it raw. Plunge this lightning rod into fresh corpses and our whelps shall do the rest.', '', 21154),
(109908, 'ruRU', 'Our whelps will grow strong gorging upon the feast you provided. You have our thanks.', '', 21154),
(109909, 'ruRU', 'You have heard of the War of the Ancients, I am sure. If you are to listen to the Highmountain tauren, they were responsible for defeating Tichondrius.\n\nBut they had help. Much help indeed. Will you listen to my story?', '', 21154),
(109910, 'ruRU', 'Honorless murlocs have overtaken the village of Morheim. I cannot abide their presence in that once-sacred place. Eradicate this filth!', '', 21154),
(109911, 'ruRU', 'Well done. I remember the one whom this village owes its name. He was a fine leader.', '', 21154),
(109912, 'ruRU', 'Esara, you really don''t want to join the Empyrean Society.', '', 21154),
(109913, 'ruRU', '', 'I don''t? Why not?', 21154),
(109914, 'ruRU', 'Their methods are a bit...distasteful. Besides, the Tirisgarde are much more powerful! We could use a mage with your experience.', '', 21154),
(109915, 'ruRU', 'Look. $n has arrived!', '', 21154),
(109916, 'ruRU', 'The children of Mimiron have crafted a clever toy they claim can harness the power of the storm. Go forth and test their handiwork in battle.', '', 21154),
(109917, 'ruRU', 'A most amusing device. But cleverness is useless without strength of arms!', '', 21154),
(109918, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Discipline priests draw upon the opposing forces of Light and Shadow, choosing when to heal and when to inflict damage. Shadow Word: Pain taints your foes with shadow energy, wounding them slowly over time.', '', 21154),
(109919, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadow Word: Pain on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109920, 'ruRU', 'Your target is now afflicted with shadow damage. Use Shadow Word: Pain whenever your target is not already affected by it.', '', 21154),
(109921, 'ruRU', 'Shadow Word: Pain has expired on your target, cast it again!', '', 21154),
(109922, 'ruRU', 'Cast Shadow Word: Pain!', '', 21154),
(109923, 'ruRU', 'The Light is a formidable ally, capable of restoring your friends or striking down foes. Penance is a potent spell that deals damage to your enemies. Use Penance whenever it is available.', '', 21154),
(109924, 'ruRU', 'Use Penance on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109925, 'ruRU', 'Penance is available!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(109926, 'ruRU', 'Cast Penance now!', '', 21154),
(109927, 'ruRU', 'The power of the Light allows you to Smite any enemy that stands before you! It is your most frequently used damage spell, best used when Penance is not available.', '', 21154),
(109928, 'ruRU', 'Use Smite on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109929, 'ruRU', 'Cast Smite!', '', 21154),
(109930, 'ruRU', 'Keep moving, wretch!', '', 21154),
(109931, 'ruRU', 'Quit dragging your feet! You belong to the Legion now!', '', 21154),
(109932, 'ruRU', 'Leviathan unit stable! Excellent work, most excellent indeed.', '', 21154),
(109933, 'ruRU', 'As a priest you have many ways to protect and restore health. One of your most useful defensive abilities is Power Word: Shield, which absorbs all damage from attacks when active. Always remember to maintain your shield during fights.', '', 21154),
(109934, 'ruRU', 'Use Power Word: Shield to prevent taking damage from this enemy.', '', 21154),
(109935, 'ruRU', 'Cast Power Word: Shield to protect yourself!', '', 21154),
(109936, 'ruRU', 'Well done! In some battles you will face multiple opponents at the same time. Fortunately, you are not defenseless in such cases. Psychic Scream terrifies nearby opponents, causing them to run away in fear.', '', 21154),
(109937, 'ruRU', 'Use Psychic Scream to prevent this group of enemies from hitting you.', '', 21154),
(109938, 'ruRU', 'Use Psychic Scream to cause fear to your enemies!', '', 21154),
(109939, 'ruRU', 'Well, friends, the good news is the download is 89% complete! But we may also be experiencing a minor case of total system failure.', '', 21154),
(109940, 'ruRU', 'You''ve taken damage, but this presents no problem for a priest. The Light gives you the power to restore the health of yourself or your allies.', '', 21154),
(109941, 'ruRU', 'Use Plea to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(109942, 'ruRU', 'Use Plea to heal yourself!', '', 21154),
(109943, 'ruRU', 'Command the forces of Shadow and Light to achieve victory!', '', 21154),
(109944, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a discipline priest.', '', 21154),
(109945, 'ruRU', 'I suppose there''s no time like the present. This will either fix everything or destroy us. I need you to press the big red button labeled ''DO NOT PUSH THIS BUTTON''.', '', 21154),
(109946, 'ruRU', 'You are not limited to only shielding yourself or an ally. A priest can also cast a shield over an entire area, protecting all allies within its boundaries.', '', 21154),
(109947, 'ruRU', 'Use Power Word: Barrier to protect these soldiers.', '', 21154),
(109948, 'ruRU', 'Healing can also be provided by the Shadow, but it comes at a cost. Shadowmend is a very powerful heal, but part of that healing will drain away over time.', '', 21154),
(109949, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadowmend to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(109950, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a windwalker monk you use your fists and your speed to overcome enemies. This builds up Chi, a resource that allows you to unleash your most powerful attacks. Start by using your primary attack, Tiger Palm, to deal damage and generate Chi.', '', 21154),
(109951, 'ruRU', 'Pressing', 'Pressing', 21154),
(109952, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger Palm on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109953, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger Palm to generate Chi!', '', 21154),
(109954, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger Palm!', '', 21154),
(109955, 'ruRU', 'Starting combat with Tiger Palm gives you enough Chi to unleash the powerful Rising Sun Kick, an attack that uses 2 Chi and deals substantial damage. Use it whenever it is available.', '', 21154),
(109956, 'ruRU', 'Use Rising Sun Kick on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109957, 'ruRU', 'Rising Sun Kick is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(109958, 'ruRU', 'Use Rising Sun Kick!', '', 21154),
(109959, 'ruRU', 'While not as powerful as Rising Sun Kick, your Blackout Kick still packs a punch... or, uh, a kick! It hits much harder than Tiger Palm, so use Blackout Kick to spend your extra Chi.', '', 21154),
(109960, 'ruRU', 'Use Blackout Kick on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109961, 'ruRU', 'Use Blackout Kick!', '', 21154),
(109962, 'ruRU', 'You have an abundance of attacks at your disposal, windwalker! Fists of Fury costs 3 Chi and does a lot of damage. It will also hit additional enemies near your target. Use Fists of Fury whenever it''s available, or if you face multiple enemies.', '', 21154),
(109963, 'ruRU', 'Use Fists of Fury on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109964, 'ruRU', 'Fists of Fury is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(109965, 'ruRU', 'Use Fists of Fury!', '', 21154),
(109966, 'ruRU', 'Monks are fast and agile, able to zip around the battlefield at will. The primary ability that gives monks their mobility is Roll, which causes you to quickly roll a good distance in whatever direction you are moving.', '', 21154),
(109967, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Roll a few times.', '', 21154),
(109968, 'ruRU', 'Your pet has been wounded! Fortunately, you can aid your trusty companion. Mend Pet will allow you to heal damage your pet has taken.', '', 21154),
(109969, 'ruRU', 'Use Mend Pet to heal your pet.', '', 21154),
(109970, 'ruRU', 'Your pet has died! When this happens, your Mend Pet ability changes to Revive Pet, which will bring your faithful companion back to life.', '', 21154),
(109971, 'ruRU', 'Call your pet!', '', 21154),
(109972, 'ruRU', 'Kill Command is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(109973, 'ruRU', 'Use Kill Command!', '', 21154),
(109974, 'ruRU', 'Dire Beast is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(109975, 'ruRU', 'Use Dire Beast!', '', 21154),
(109976, 'ruRU', 'Use Cobra Shot!', '', 21154),
(109977, 'ruRU', 'Bestial Wrath is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(109978, 'ruRU', 'Use Bestial Wrath!', '', 21154),
(109979, 'ruRU', 'Your pet is hurt! Use Mend Pet!', '', 21154),
(109980, 'ruRU', 'Use Multi-Shot to damage multiple enemies at once!', '', 21154),
(109981, 'ruRU', 'Divine Shield will completely protect you from all attacks for a short period of time, so save it for emergencies.', '', 21154),
(109982, 'ruRU', 'The roots run deep. All will succumb to the Nightmare!', '', 21154),
(109983, 'ruRU', 'I have seen the Nightmare. The Emerald Dream will perish.', '', 21154),
(109984, 'ruRU', 'Excellent! Always remember to use Flame Shock to keep your enemies burning.', '', 21154),
(109985, 'ruRU', 'I return to the Nightmare... What once was light is darkness. Come with me... come with me...', '', 21154),
(109986, 'ruRU', 'Use your Lightning Bolt on the Target Dummy until you have the maximum amount of Maelstrom, then use Earth Shock.', '', 21154),
(109987, 'ruRU', 'Very well. Once we clear an area, reinforcements will secure it. Down we go.', '', 21154),
(109988, 'ruRU', 'You can call upon the earth itself to defend you and your allies in battle.', '', 21154),
(109989, 'ruRU', 'Use Fire Elemental if you need a boost of damage in a fight!', '', 21154),
(109990, 'ruRU', 'Use Earth Elemental to summon an earthen protector for a short period.', '', 21154),
(109991, 'ruRU', 'When facing multiple enemies, you can shake the very ground beneath their feet to damage several targets at once.', '', 21154),
(109992, 'ruRU', 'Use Earthquake Totem against multiple foes.', '', 21154),
(109993, 'ruRU', 'As a shaman you can commune with wolf spirits and take on their form. While this doesn''t give you new combat abilities, it does allow you to move faster.', '', 21154),
(109994, 'ruRU', 'Practice moving around in Ghost Wolf form.', '', 21154),
(109995, 'ruRU', 'Shamans are valuable allies, as they can use their abilities to empower themselves as well as their party and raid members.', '', 21154),
(109996, 'ruRU', 'Use Heroism to temporarily increase your Haste, which speeds up your attacks and spell casts.', '', 21154),
(109997, 'ruRU', 'If you become surrounded in combat, use Thunderstorm to knock enemies back and give yourself some breathing room.', '', 21154),
(109998, 'ruRU', 'Use Thunderstorm to knock away the enemies surrounding you.', '', 21154),
(109999, 'ruRU', 'Use Flame Shock to burn your enemy!', '', 21154),
(110000, 'ruRU', 'Use Flame Shock!', '', 21154),
(110001, 'ruRU', 'Only use Flame Shock when it''s about to expire!', '', 21154),
(110002, 'ruRU', 'Use Lava Burst while your enemy is burning!', '', 21154),
(110003, 'ruRU', 'Use Lava Burst!', '', 21154),
(110004, 'ruRU', 'Using Lava Burst after your enemy is burning from Flame Shock increases its damage!', '', 21154),
(110005, 'ruRU', 'Use Lightning Bolt!', '', 21154),
(110006, 'ruRU', 'You are at maximum Maelstrom! Use Earth Shock!', '', 21154),
(110007, 'ruRU', 'Use Earth Shock!', '', 21154),
(110008, 'ruRU', 'Wait until you are at maximum Maelstrom to use Earth Shock!', '', 21154),
(110009, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies, try using Chain Lightning!', '', 21154),
(110010, 'ruRU', 'Heal yourself with Healing Surge!', '', 21154),
(110011, 'ruRU', 'Now would be a great time to use Fire Elemental!', '', 21154),
(110012, 'ruRU', 'Now would be a great time to use Earth Elemental!', '', 21154),
(110013, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies, try using Earthquake Totem!', '', 21154),
(110014, 'ruRU', 'Use Bloodlust to temporarily increase your Haste, which speeds up your attacks and spell casts.', '', 21154),
(110015, 'ruRU', 'Use Thunderstorm to knock enemies away!', '', 21154),
(110016, 'ruRU', 'Download complete! Splendid work, positively splendid. Come on over to the control console.', '', 21154),
(110017, 'ruRU', 'Any lout with a hammer and tongs can bang steel. It takes a master craftsman to weave the very essence of the arcane into one''s creations, to forge weapons of cunning as well as brute strength.', '', 21154),
(110018, 'ruRU', 'Though your kind has brought honor to these shores, some among you bring darkness as well! Even now, a plague born of a vile hybrid of the Legion and the Old Gods seeps into my sacred soil. Cleanse it!', '', 21154),
(110019, 'ruRU', 'Be warned! I will not tolerate such corruption in my lands.', '', 21154),
(110020, 'ruRU', 'Yes... yes, I see. Oh. No, no, no. Not good. Not good at all.', '', 21154),
(110021, 'ruRU', 'What is it? Where''s Prustaga headed?', '', 21154),
(110022, 'ruRU', 'Thorim''s throne at the Temple of Storms. I''ll explain on the way. We don''t have much time!', '', 21154),
(110023, 'ruRU', 'Roll, monk, roll!', '', 21154),
(110024, 'ruRU', 'Taking damage is part of battle, but as a monk you can tap the spiritual mists to heal yourself or an ally. Use Effuse to heal your wounds.', '', 21154),
(110025, 'ruRU', 'Use Effuse to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110026, 'ruRU', 'Heal yourself with Effuse!', '', 21154),
(110027, 'ruRU', 'Let us make our way to the platform above.', '', 21154),
(110028, 'ruRU', '', 'I don''t see anything unusual about this brazier. It looks to be in pretty good shape for something so ancient!', 21154),
(110029, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the savagery and cunning of a feral druid!', '', 21154),
(110030, 'ruRU', 'Your allies spill the blood of their rivals upon the field of battle. Join them and prove your valor!', '', 21154),
(110031, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as an unholy death knight.', '', 21154),
(110032, 'ruRU', 'Roll is not your only ability for mobility. Windwalker monks can also launch themselves through the air, flying at their targets. Use Flying Serpent Kick to launch yourself at your enemy. Using it a second time while you are in the air will end your flight and deal damage to enemies nearby.', '', 21154),
(110033, 'ruRU', 'Use Flying Serpent Kick to travel to the target dummy and damage it.', '', 21154),
(110034, 'ruRU', 'Use Flying Serpent Kick a second time to stop your movement early.', '', 21154),
(110035, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you might get in over your head, facing more enemies than you can handle. Take one enemy out of the fight by paralyzing him! Paralyze will knock out an enemy for a short time, but the foe will recover if he takes any damage.', '', 21154),
(110036, 'ruRU', 'Paralyze the soldier who attacks you.', '', 21154),
(110037, 'ruRU', 'Fights aren''t always fair... or are they? If you find yourself facing three or more opponents, tap your inner spirit to duplicate yourself, making you your own ally! Your allied selves will attack enemies automatically.', '', 21154),
(110038, 'ruRU', 'Use Storm, Earth, and Fire to attack all three of these target dummies at once.', '', 21154),
(110039, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies! Try using Storm, Earth, and Fire!', '', 21154),
(110040, 'ruRU', 'Your monk training has taught you the precision necessary to strike an enemy''s pressure points. Touch of Death deals massive damage, but takes a short time to take effect. Use it whenever you meet someone you don''t like, although you might want to save it for your toughest enemies!', '', 21154),
(110041, 'ruRU', 'Use Touch of Death on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110042, 'ruRU', 'Well fought! You have shown yourself to be worthy.', '', 21154),
(110043, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a feral druid your main weapon is shapeshifting. In Cat Form, your claws and fangs rip and bleed your opponents. Soon they''ll be weak enough for you to go for the throat with a mighty finishing move. Use Cat Form to become a cat.', '', 21154),
(110044, 'ruRU', 'Use Cat Form and assume the form of a cat.', '', 21154),
(110045, 'ruRU', 'You need to be in Cat Form to fight!', '', 21154),
(110046, 'ruRU', 'You are not in Cat Form!', '', 21154),
(110047, 'ruRU', 'As a cat you can move with uncanny stealth, allowing you to approach your enemies undetected. Prowl puts you in stealth mode.', '', 21154),
(110048, 'ruRU', 'Use Prowl to enter stealth.', '', 21154),
(110049, 'ruRU', 'Stealth lasts until you cancel it, attack, or take damage.', '', 21154),
(110050, 'ruRU', 'Your primary attack is Shred. Though powerful on its own, using Shred from stealth increases its damage, so try to start a fight while you are in stealth.', '', 21154),
(110051, 'ruRU', 'Use Shred on the target dummy from stealth, then use it once to deal damage out of stealth.', '', 21154),
(110052, 'ruRU', 'Use Shred to generate combo points!', '', 21154),
(110053, 'ruRU', 'Use Shred!', '', 21154),
(110054, 'ruRU', 'Our ascension is at hand. Have you brought us something worthy?', 'Our ascension is at hand. Have you brought us something worthy?', 21154),
(110055, 'ruRU', 'Once you''ve ambushed your prey, it''s time to weaken them. Rake will cause your target to bleed, wounding them over time. Your Shred ability also deals extra damage to bleeding targets, so these are great abilities to use together.', '', 21154),
(110056, 'ruRU', 'Use Rake on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110057, 'ruRU', 'Rake inflicts its damage over time, so you don''t need to use it again until your target is no longer affected by it.', '', 21154),
(110058, 'ruRU', 'Use Rake!', '', 21154),
(110059, 'ruRU', 'Both your Shred and Rake abilities generate combo points which can fuel powerful finishing moves. Ferocious Bite is a finishing move that deals increased damage the more combo points you have. Try to use it when you have a full 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(110060, 'ruRU', 'When you have 5 combo points, use Ferocious Bite on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110061, 'ruRU', 'You have 5 combo points! Use Ferocious Bite now!', '', 21154),
(110062, 'ruRU', 'Use Ferocious Bite!', '', 21154),
(110063, 'ruRU', 'Most of your attacks require energy to use. You might find yourself low on energy at times, rendering you unable to use any abilities. Tiger''s Fury restores some energy and also increases your damage for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110064, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger''s Fury to restore some energy and then attack the target dummy with Shred.', '', 21154),
(110065, 'ruRU', 'You''re low on energy! Use Tiger''s Fury!', '', 21154),
(110066, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger''s Fury!', '', 21154),
(110067, 'ruRU', 'Tougher enemies may require a diverse set of abilities to overcome. As an alternative to Ferocious Bite, Rip can be used to deal bleeding damage over time to your target, and is a good ability to spend combo points on early in a fight. Like Ferocious Bite, Rip is a finishing move, and is best used when you have 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(110068, 'ruRU', 'Use Rip on the target dummy with five combo points.', '', 21154),
(110069, 'ruRU', 'You have 5 combo points! Use Rip!', '', 21154),
(110070, 'ruRU', 'Use Rip!', '', 21154),
(110071, 'ruRU', 'Ever needed to quickly get out of a sticky situation? Druids excel at doing this. Dash increases your movement speed significantly for a short time. It can''t be used often, so save it for when you really need it.', '', 21154),
(110072, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Dash to increase your movement speed.', '', 21154),
(110073, 'ruRU', 'As a druid you also have the ability to call on the powers of nature for a variety of other abilities, like healing! After you''ve taken damage, use Healing Touch to restore your health.', '', 21154),
(110074, 'ruRU', 'Use Healing Touch to restore yourself to full health.', '', 21154),
(110075, 'ruRU', 'Heal yourself with Healing Touch!', '', 21154),
(110076, 'ruRU', 'Using spells will usually pull you out of shapeshift forms. Don''t forget to return to cat form for combat.', '', 21154),
(110077, 'ruRU', 'Use Cat Form.', '', 21154),
(110078, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you need an enemy to stay put so you can close the distance to them... or make a hasty retreat. Entangling Roots will cause plant roots to spring from the ground and hold the target in place for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110079, 'ruRU', 'Use Entangling Roots to root my soldier to the ground.', '', 21154),
(110080, 'ruRU', 'We are preparing to ascend. I hope Marlan finds your gift acceptable so you can join us.', 'We are preparing to ascend. I hope Marlan finds your gift acceptable so you can join us.', 21154),
(110081, 'ruRU', 'Try using Entangling Roots to immobilize your target!', '', 21154),
(110082, 'ruRU', 'Try to root the target before it can reach you! Let''s try again!', '', 21154),
(110083, 'ruRU', 'Cast Entangling Roots!', '', 21154),
(110084, 'ruRU', 'When in Cat Form you can rely on the instincts of an animal to help pull you through a tough fight. Survival Instincts reduces incoming damage for a short time. Save it for when you really need it!', '', 21154),
(110085, 'ruRU', 'Use Survival Instincts to reduce incoming damage.', '', 21154),
(110086, 'ruRU', 'You''re taking a lot of damage! Use Survival Instincts!', '', 21154),
(110087, 'ruRU', 'So the stories are true - you''ve recovered Felo''melorn!$b$bShattered during the third war, Prince Kael''thas ordered its repair. Elven blades grow stronger with each reforging, but only in the hands of the finest craftsmen.$b$bI have never seen such a wonder. May I hold it?', '', 21154),
(110088, 'ruRU', 'Thrash isn''t your only tool for fighting multiple enemies. Swipe deals damage to all nearby foes, but that damage is increased if your targets are bleeding. It''s a good idea to use Thrash and Swipe together.', '', 21154),
(110089, 'ruRU', 'Use Swipe to damage several enemies at once.', '', 21154),
(110090, 'ruRU', 'You''re fighting multiple enemies, try using Swipe!', '', 21154),
(110091, 'ruRU', 'Now use Swipe!', '', 21154),
(110092, 'ruRU', 'Using Thrash then Swipe is a great combination!', '', 21154),
(110093, 'ruRU', 'When fighting multiple enemies at once a feral druid can become a whirlwind of fangs and claws, damaging everything around them. Thrash will damage all nearby enemies, causing them to bleed for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110094, 'ruRU', 'Use Thrash to damage several enemies at once.', '', 21154),
(110095, 'ruRU', 'Thrash continues to damage your foes for a short period, so you don''t need to use it again until your targets stops being affected by it.', '', 21154),
(110096, 'ruRU', 'You may. But only for a moment.', 'You may. But only for a moment.', 21154),
(110097, 'ruRU', 'Rake has expired on your target! Use it again!', '', 21154),
(110098, 'ruRU', 'You''re fighting multiple enemies. Try using Thrash!', '', 21154),
(110099, 'ruRU', 'Starting a fight from stealth is more effective. Use Prowl to enter stealth!', '', 21154),
(110100, 'ruRU', '', 'That Pearl of Arcane Wisdom you found is really impressive! I just brought an old spell book I stole from the Zul''Gurub trolls.', 21154),
(110101, 'ruRU', '', 'Have you traveled much, $n? I bet you''ve visited some pretty amazing places!', 21154),
(110102, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As an unholy death knight you command the powers of disease and death. Disease wears your enemy down while your strong melee attacks finish them off. But your greatest ally is death itself. Raise Dead will animate a corpse to serve as your ghoulish minion. You should always try to have a minion with you.', '', 21154),
(110103, 'ruRU', 'Use Raise Dead to summon your minion.', '', 21154),
(110104, 'ruRU', 'The best way to start a fight as a death knight is to infect your enemy with a host of diseases from a distance. Outbreak will deal damage over time and unleashes a Virulent Plague that spreads to nearby enemies.', '', 21154),
(110105, 'ruRU', 'Use Outbreak on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110106, 'ruRU', 'Now that your enemy is reeling from a miasma of plagues, it''s time to strike up close. Festering Strike deals damage and inflicts Festering Wounds on your target.', '', 21154),
(110107, 'ruRU', 'Use Festering Strike on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110108, 'ruRU', 'Oh, that looks like it hurts! After infecting your target with Festering Strike, you are ready to burst the lesions you''ve caused using Scourge Strike! Festering Strike followed by Scourge Strike is a one-two punch few enemies can withstand.', '', 21154),
(110109, 'ruRU', 'Argent Crusaders, secure this area! We will press on!', '', 21154),
(110110, 'ruRU', 'Use Scourge Strike on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110111, 'ruRU', 'Try to only use Scourge Strike when your target is affected by Festering Wounds.', '', 21154),
(110112, 'ruRU', 'Your attacks build Runic Power that can be used to cast Death Coil, a spell that hurls a blast of unholy energy at your target and restores energy to your ghoul minion.', '', 21154),
(110113, 'ruRU', 'Use Death Coil on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110114, 'ruRU', 'Your attacks sometimes allow you to cast Death Coil without costing Runic Power. Take advantage of this when you can.', '', 21154),
(110115, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ve always loved magic. I saw the Great Akamazamak as a child and I wanted to be just like him!', 21154),
(110116, 'ruRU', 'Some foes would prefer to keep a death knight at arm''s length. Death Grip allows you to reach out to a distant target and pull them toward you. No enemy can escape your icy grasp!', '', 21154),
(110117, 'ruRU', 'Use Death Grip to pull my soldier to you.', '', 21154),
(110118, 'ruRU', 'Death Grip can be used from a good distance away. Try moving further away from the target and using it.', '', 21154),
(110119, 'ruRU', 'Being an unholy death knight means you rarely need to be outnumbered. Army of the Dead raises a swarm of ghouls to attack anything and everything near you. This powerful ability cannot be used often, so save it for an emergency.', '', 21154),
(110120, 'ruRU', 'Use Army of the Dead in the coming fight when you need it.', '', 21154),
(110121, 'ruRU', 'Show me you''ve mastered the powers of darkness as only a death knight can!', '', 21154),
(110122, 'ruRU', 'Your undead minion is a valuable asset in battle. Dark Transformation allows you to temporarily transform your ghoul into a hulking monstrosity with increased power and abilities. Try it out!', '', 21154),
(110123, 'ruRU', 'Use Dark Transformation to empower your ghoul.', '', 21154),
(110124, 'ruRU', 'Ah, Felo''melorn. The Flamestrike! Such craftsmanship, such elegance...', '', 21154),
(110125, 'ruRU', 'As a death knight, you control the battlefield! Use Death and Decay to corrupt the ground beneath your feet, dealing damage to all foes in the affected area and empowering some of your attacks to hit additional targets.', '', 21154),
(110126, 'ruRU', 'Use Death and Decay to dispatch the group of minions.', '', 21154),
(110127, 'ruRU', 'This is not some brutish cleaver for the hacking of flesh. It is the slender blade of a tactician. Strands of arcane energy have been woven into the steel with each fold. I can feel its heat radiating down my arms. Magnificent!', '', 21154),
(110128, 'ruRU', 'When taking excessive damage in battle, Death Strike can help even the odds. Its dark power damages your foe and recovers a portion of your health.', '', 21154),
(110129, 'ruRU', 'Use Death Strike on the target to recover some of your health.', '', 21154),
(110130, 'ruRU', 'Thank you, $n. I have labored a hundred lifetimes and have not seen its like.', '', 21154),
(110131, 'ruRU', 'Your minion is dead. Cast Raise Dead to summon a new minion.', '', 21154),
(110132, 'ruRU', 'Outbreak has expired from your target, use it now!', '', 21154),
(110133, 'ruRU', 'Cast Outbreak!', '', 21154),
(110134, 'ruRU', 'Your target is not infested with Festering Wounds. Use Festering Strike now!', '', 21154),
(110135, 'ruRU', 'Use Festering Strike!', '', 21154),
(110136, 'ruRU', 'Use Scourge Strike!', '', 21154),
(110137, 'ruRU', 'Using Scourge Strike after Festering Strike is a potent combination!', '', 21154),
(110138, 'ruRU', 'Death Coil is free!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110139, 'ruRU', 'Use Death Coil!', '', 21154),
(110140, 'ruRU', 'Now is a good time to cast Army of the Dead!', '', 21154),
(110141, 'ruRU', 'Now is a good time to cast Dark Transformation!', '', 21154),
(110142, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies. Try using Death and Decay!', '', 21154),
(110143, 'ruRU', 'You''re low on health! Use Death Strike!', '', 21154),
(110144, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a frost mage you excel at controlling the battlefield by freezing enemies in place as ice and hail pummel them into submission. Frost Mages can call forth a water elemental pet, so we''ll start there.', '', 21154),
(110145, 'ruRU', 'Use Summon Water Elemental to summon your pet.', '', 21154),
(110146, 'ruRU', 'Your most fundamental and reliable attack is Frostbolt. This long-range attack will damage and slow your enemies, and has a chance to empower other attacks.', '', 21154),
(110147, 'ruRU', 'Use Frostbolt on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110148, 'ruRU', 'What are you still doin'' here? Get!', '', 21154),
(110149, 'ruRU', 'Now we''ll take a look at Ice Lance. It''s similar to Frostbolt, but can be cast instantly, albeit for less damage.', '', 21154),
(110150, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110151, 'ruRU', 'But Ice Lance''s real power lies in using it against a frozen target, which greatly increases its damage.', '', 21154),
(110152, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance on the frozen target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110153, 'ruRU', 'There is one more way that Ice Lance can be used to maximize its power. Frostbolt occasionally triggers the Fingers of Frost effect, which gives a huge boost to Ice Lance damage. Let''s test it out.', '', 21154),
(110154, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance on the target dummy while the Fingers of Frost effect is active.', '', 21154),
(110155, 'ruRU', 'Feet don''t fail me now!', '', 21154),
(110156, 'ruRU', 'Use Frostbolt on the target dummy until Fingers of Frost is triggered, then use Ice Lance.', '', 21154),
(110157, 'ruRU', 'Another potent spell you can wield is Frozen Orb. Cast this spell whenever it is available, as it can make your Ice Lance more powerful. Be careful, though, as it hits all enemies in its path, not just your target.', '', 21154),
(110158, 'ruRU', 'Use Frozen Orb on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110159, 'ruRU', 'The battlefield can be a dangerous place, so moving about is crucial to your survival. But using your legs is so mundane! Fortunately, you have a spell that befits a master of the magical arts. Blink allows you to teleport a short distance to avoid danger or close in on an enemy.', '', 21154),
(110160, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Blink.', '', 21154),
(110161, 'ruRU', 'What if you could freeze foes in their tracks, preventing them from even reaching you? Frost Nova freezes nearby enemies in place, allowing you to move away and destroy them safely. For now, let''s just practice freezing them in place.', '', 21154),
(110162, 'ruRU', 'Freeze this enemy using Frost Nova.', '', 21154),
(110163, 'ruRU', 'Remember that Ice Lance does extra damage to frozen targets, so using Frost Nova and Ice Lance together is a powerful tactic.', '', 21154),
(110164, 'ruRU', 'Mages are masters of dealing damage to many enemies at once. You can pelt a target location with shards of ice by using a potent spell called Blizzard. Great name, don''t you think?', '', 21154),
(110165, 'ruRU', 'Use Blizzard to dispatch this group of enemies.', '', 21154),
(110166, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the fury of the elements as only a shaman can!', '', 21154),
(110167, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as an enhancement shaman.', '', 21154),
(110168, 'ruRU', 'Despite your best efforts, you may not be able to prevent an enemy from reaching you. In those cases, a little bit of extra protection is needed. Ice Barrier creates a shield of ice to absorb enemy attacks.', '', 21154),
(110169, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Barrier to reduce incoming damage.', '', 21154),
(110170, 'ruRU', 'Need to get out of a fight in a hurry? Invisibility is a great spell for getting out of a sticky situation. Use it and enemies will be unable to target you, letting you escape form combat. But be careful! It doesn''t last long.', '', 21154),
(110171, 'ruRU', 'Use Invisibility to escape combat.', '', 21154),
(110172, 'ruRU', 'Your Water Elemental has died. Cast Summon Water Elemental to call it back!', '', 21154),
(110173, 'ruRU', 'Use Frostbolt!', '', 21154),
(110174, 'ruRU', 'Fingers of Frost has triggered! Use Ice Lance now!', '', 21154),
(110175, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance!', '', 21154),
(110176, 'ruRU', 'Your target is frozen! Use Ice Lance!', '', 21154),
(110177, 'ruRU', 'Frozen Orb is available! Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110178, 'ruRU', 'Use Frozen Orb!', '', 21154),
(110179, 'ruRU', 'You''re under attack! Use Frost Nova to immobilize your opponent!', '', 21154),
(110180, 'ruRU', 'You need to freeze your enemy in place before they reach you.', '', 21154),
(110181, 'ruRU', 'Use Frost Nova!', '', 21154),
(110182, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies. Try casting Blizzard!', '', 21154),
(110183, 'ruRU', 'You''re taking damage! Cast Ice Barrier!', '', 21154),
(110184, 'ruRU', 'You''re in trouble! Use Invisibility!', '', 21154),
(110185, 'ruRU', '', 'Life never gets any easier around here.', 21154),
(110186, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As an enhancement shaman you channel the elemental forces directly into your weapons to make yourself a furious melee combatant, beating down your foes with the power of flame, earth, and storm. The first attack we''ll try is Flametongue, which emblazes your weapons and scorches your enemy with fire.', '', 21154),
(110187, 'ruRU', 'Use Flametongue on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110188, 'ruRU', 'Now that your weapons are burning, you can focus on your primary attack. Rockbiter empowers your weapons with the forces of earth to deal damage.', '', 21154),
(110189, 'ruRU', 'Use Rockbiter on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110190, 'ruRU', 'Using Rockbiter generates Maelstrom, a resource that powers stronger attacks. Lava Lash uses Maelstrom to charge your off-hand weapon with lava, allowing you to deal a mighty blow.', '', 21154),
(110191, 'ruRU', 'Use Lava Lash on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110192, 'ruRU', 'Your most powerful Maelstrom-fueled ability is Stormstrike. This attack costs more resources, but deals more damage as well. Thankfully, your melee attacks have a chance to trigger Stormfury, decreasing the cost. Try to use Stormstrike whenever Stormfury triggers.', '', 21154),
(110193, 'ruRU', 'Use Stormstrike on the target dummy after Stormfury triggers.', '', 21154),
(110194, 'ruRU', 'Use Stormstrike now!', '', 21154),
(110195, 'ruRU', 'As a shaman you share a kinship with animal spirits such as wolves. Should you find yourself in trouble during combat, you can summon two feral wolf spirits to fight at your side.', '', 21154),
(110196, 'ruRU', 'Use Feral Spirit if you need to boost your damage in a fight!', '', 21154),
(110197, 'ruRU', 'If you are fighting multiple enemies, it is time to unleash the full fury of the storm! Crash Lightning deals damage to all targets in front of you. Hitting multiple enemies empowers your weapons, dealing even more damage!', '', 21154),
(110198, 'ruRU', 'Use Crash Lightning to dispatch this group of enemies.', '', 21154),
(110199, 'ruRU', 'If you find yourself taking too much punishment in a fight, Shamanistic Rage reduces incoming damage for a short period of time. Try it!', '', 21154),
(110200, 'ruRU', 'Use Shamanistic Rage to reduce incoming damage.', '', 21154),
(110201, 'ruRU', 'Your Flametongue buff has expired! Use Flametongue!', '', 21154),
(110202, 'ruRU', 'Use Flametongue!', '', 21154),
(110203, 'ruRU', 'An entry from someone named... Abercrombie. He asked me to read the following: ''I fooled the bearer of this note into announcing my latest, most dire creation!'' Weird guy, that one.', '', 21154),
(110204, 'ruRU', 'Use Rockbiter to generate Maelstrom!', '', 21154),
(110205, 'ruRU', 'Use Rockbiter!', '', 21154),
(110206, 'ruRU', 'I guess Stitches just... unraveled. Get it? Stitches? Unraveled? Man, I''m on fire!', '', 21154),
(110207, 'ruRU', 'Lava Lash is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110208, 'ruRU', 'Use Lava Lash!', '', 21154),
(110209, 'ruRU', 'Stormfury has triggered! Use Stormstrike now!', '', 21154),
(110210, 'ruRU', 'Use Stormstrike!', '', 21154),
(110211, 'ruRU', 'Now is a good time to try Feral Spirit!', '', 21154),
(110212, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies. Try using Crash Lightning!', '', 21154),
(110213, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a balance druid the sun, moon, and stars are your allies, enabling you to unleash these primal powers upon your enemies. You can shapeshift into Moonkin form, which increases both your damage and defense.', '', 21154),
(110214, 'ruRU', 'Use Moonkin Form and assume the form of a wildkin.', '', 21154),
(110215, 'ruRU', 'You wield the very power of night and day against your foes. Moonfire and Sunfire represent that power. These attacks deal their damage over time, and either makes an excellent start to a battle.', '', 21154),
(110216, 'ruRU', 'Use Moonfire and Sunfire on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110217, 'ruRU', 'Both these attacks deal damage over time. Once cast, you don''t need to cast them again until their effect on the target has expired.', '', 21154),
(110218, 'ruRU', 'Once your enemy is taking damage from your other attacks, it''s time to unleash Solar Wrath. Solar Wrath is a ranged ability that deals damage and generates Astral Power, a resource used to fuel more powerful attacks.', '', 21154),
(110219, 'ruRU', 'Use Solar Wrath on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110220, 'ruRU', 'One of your most potent attacks, Starsurge unleashes a surge of stellar energy at your target. Starsurge costs Astral Power, so use Solar Wrath to build up your reserves.', '', 21154),
(110221, 'ruRU', 'I''ll take care of this!', '', 21154),
(110222, 'ruRU', 'Use Solar Wrath on the target dummy until you have enough Astral Power to cast Starsurge.', '', 21154),
(110223, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you need an enemy to stay put so you can close the distance to them... or make a hasty retreat. Entangling Roots will cause plant roots to spring from the ground and hold the target in place for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110224, 'ruRU', 'Use Entangling Roots to root my soldier to the ground.', '', 21154),
(110225, 'ruRU', 'Show me that you can harness the power of the universe itself as a druid!', '', 21154),
(110226, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a feral druid.', '', 21154),
(110227, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a balance druid.', '', 21154),
(110228, 'ruRU', 'Need a boost of damage? Look to the stars! Celestial Alignment causes the celestial bodies to align, increasing the damage of your solar and lunar spells for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110229, 'ruRU', 'Use Celestial Alignment to increase damage, then use Solar Wrath on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110230, 'ruRU', 'A balance druid is well equipped to face multiple opponents at once. Lunar Strike deals damage directly to your target, but also deals damage to nearby foes.', '', 21154),
(110231, 'ruRU', 'Use Lunar Strike to dispatch this group of enemies.', '', 21154),
(110232, 'ruRU', 'You are not in Moonkin form! Use Moonkin Form to maximize your damage!', '', 21154),
(110233, 'ruRU', 'Moonfire has expired on your target! Cast Moonfire on your target!', '', 21154),
(110234, 'ruRU', 'Sunfire has expired on your target! Cast Sunfire on your target!', '', 21154),
(110235, 'ruRU', 'Cast Moonfire!', '', 21154),
(110236, 'ruRU', 'Cast Sunfire!', '', 21154),
(110237, 'ruRU', 'Cast Solar Wrath to generate Astral Power!', '', 21154),
(110238, 'ruRU', 'Cast Solar Wrath!', '', 21154),
(110239, 'ruRU', 'Starsurge is available! Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110240, 'ruRU', 'Cast Starsurge!', '', 21154),
(110241, 'ruRU', 'Try using Entangling Roots to immobilize your target!', '', 21154),
(110242, 'ruRU', 'Try to root the target before it can reach you! Let''s try again!', '', 21154),
(110243, 'ruRU', 'Cast Entangling Roots!', '', 21154),
(110244, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies, try using Lunar Strike!', '', 21154),
(110245, 'ruRU', 'Nothing you cannot handle!', '', 21154),
(110246, 'ruRU', 'That is a most... unusual murloc. There''s something familiar about him, but I can''t quite place it. Could you take a closer look?', '', 21154),
(110247, 'ruRU', 'Why did you want to join the Empyrean Society?', 'Why did you want to join the Empyrean Society?', 21154),
(110248, 'ruRU', 'It seems all creatures are susceptible to the Legion''s corruption. No matter how... small.', '', 21154),
(110249, 'ruRU', 'My patrol... they''re dead! All dead!', 'My patrol... they''re dead! All dead!', 21154),
(110250, 'ruRU', 'They came out of nowhere! Be careful!', 'They came out of nowhere! Be careful!', 21154),
(110251, 'ruRU', 'My thanks. Allow me to repay you with my service.', 'My thanks. Allow me to repay you with my service.', 21154),
(110252, 'ruRU', '', 'Magic isn''t practiced by many goblins in Booty Bay, and I was pretty much the best mage around. Okay, so I was the only mage, but that doesn''t mean I can''t hold my own amongst the best!\n\nAnyway, a few weeks ago, an E.S.E.M.A. recruiter arrived in town and offered to teach me some new spells if I joined up, so I figured, why not? She didn''t mention that I''d have to dye my hair black, though...', 21154),
(110253, 'ruRU', 'My blade is yours, $n.', 'My blade is yours, $n.', 21154),
(110254, 'ruRU', 'What did she tell you about their activities?', 'What did she tell you about their activities?', 21154),
(110255, 'ruRU', 'Don''t be fooled! That creature is not one of our brood. Tread carefully, hero.', '', 21154),
(110256, 'ruRU', 'Tend to your companions'' wounds. You did well.', '', 21154),
(110257, 'ruRU', '', 'She said E.S.E.M.A. searches the world for rare forms of magic to study. Pretty exciting, right? \n\nShe did mention something about "ascending to the next level," which struck me as a bit odd. But, I figured it referred to society leadership stuff and I''d learn more about it once I became a member.', 21154),
(110258, 'ruRU', 'This chasm oozes darkness... Light protect us! That thing has what we need. Prepare yourselves, friends.', '', 21154),
(110259, 'ruRU', '', 'An infestation of leyworms has broken out in the Leyhollow caves! If you plug their tunnels with heavy stones, it should help contain them.', 21154),
(110260, 'ruRU', '', 'What''s that?! One of the bigger worms is burrowing through! Stand ready!', 21154),
(110261, 'ruRU', '', 'I believe that will stop their influx for now. Thank you, champion.', 21154),
(110262, 'ruRU', 'This area is very unstable now thanks to the previous visitors. We need to kill that thing to get what we need, but I''m not sure what it will do to our surroundings.\n\nIt would be best to kill it quick and get out of here. Say the word, $n.', '', 21154),
(110263, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\inv_pet_broom.blp:20|t %s calls Scrubbers to |cFFF00000|Hspell:207513|h[Tidy Up]|h|r.', '', 21154),
(110264, 'ruRU', 'What''s that sound?', '', 21154),
(110265, 'ruRU', 'Nicely done, but those demons won''t give up so easily. Stand ready!', '', 21154),
(110266, 'ruRU', 'What is that I hear?', '', 21154),
(110267, 'ruRU', 'Disturbances are punishable by death! Do not let this happen again!', '', 21154),
(110268, 'ruRU', 'Next time I will see you withered for wasting my time!', '', 21154),
(110269, 'ruRU', 'The Nightmare has manifested in a physical form and consumed most of our home. We had nowhere else to go, so we headed east.', '', 21154),
(110270, 'ruRU', 'We have decided with some hesitance to settle here. It is not easily that we leave Val''Sharah.', '', 21154),
(110271, 'ruRU', '', 'This is no small feat. We will seek the blessings of the local wildlife so that the moonwell may endure.', 21154),
(110272, 'ruRU', '', 'Do not worry, we will be beside you the whole way.', 21154),
(110273, 'ruRU', 'As a shaman, you are able to coalesce primal elemental forces into physical form to aid you in battle.', '', 21154),
(110274, 'ruRU', 'The Gaze of the Legion has spotted you!', '', 21154),
(110275, 'ruRU', 'The Aerial Command Unit can take you right to the temple. Hop in!', '', 21154),
(110276, 'ruRU', 'Greetings, illustrious guests! Welcome back to Ulduar! The Speaker is expecting you.', '', 21154),
(110277, 'ruRU', 'With the corruption of the Nightmare spreading, I fear for the wildlife of Val''Sharah. I feel some would be safer in your care.', '', 21154),
(110278, 'ruRU', '"The Speaker"? We''ve come to see me brother Magni, ye infernal contraption!', '', 21154),
(110279, 'ruRU', 'While trapping animals can be traumatic, it''s a far better fate than what awaited them. I wish you and your new companions well.', '', 21154),
(110280, 'ruRU', 'Forgive me. I was referring to his current designation. The one you once called Magni Bronzebeard is now known to us as the Speaker.', '', 21154),
(110281, 'ruRU', 'Oh, fer all the... Just take us to ''im!', '', 21154),
(110282, 'ruRU', 'It will be my pleasure, Brann Bronzebeard. Right this way!', '', 21154),
(110283, 'ruRU', 'Lost Owlkitten slowly raises its head and looks around.', '', 21154),
(110284, 'ruRU', 'Lost Owlkitten spots you and scampers away in fear!', '', 21154),
(110285, 'ruRU', '$n! Is it true? Do you wield Felo''melorn? Come, speak with me!', '', 21154),
(110286, 'ruRU', 'I will scout ahead.', '', 21154),
(110287, 'ruRU', '$n - is it true that you carry Kael''thas''s former blade? Come closer!', '', 21154),
(110288, 'ruRU', 'Felo''melorn! A blade fit for royalty. In the hands of Anasterian Sunstrider, a thousand Amani trolls fell before its fury.', '', 21154),
(110289, 'ruRU', 'Ah! It is hot to the touch! How do you even...? No matter. I see this blade is in good hands. Thank you, $n, for allowing me to touch a piece of my peoples'' history.', '', 21154),
(110290, 'ruRU', 'I fear if we dally much longer, those giants will pound Nar''thalas into the sea.', '', 21154),
(110291, 'ruRU', 'Destroy the monster! For the Light!', '', 21154),
(110292, 'ruRU', 'The stories are true. A hero once more wields Felo''melorn! I thought the blade lost in the wastes of Icecrown. As relics go, it predates the War of the Ancients. May I... may I see it?', '', 21154),
(110293, 'ruRU', '', 'Watch yourself, Andoren. Belloc would be displeased to see you fraternizing with the Alliance...', 21154),
(110294, 'ruRU', 'Pity you aren''t joining Thorim under more pleasant circumstances. He''s quite the animal lover himself! Always going on about those wolves of his.', '', 21154),
(110295, 'ruRU', 'Aye, it''ll be nice to be around one of our own. Even if he is a bit tall for my likin''.', '', 21154),
(110296, 'ruRU', 'Indeed, Bronzebeard. Now hold on! I''m taking you in.', '', 21154),
(110297, 'ruRU', 'Bronzebeard! Back again, I see! Hati has missed you, as has Skoll. Skoll? Bah! Where has that worg run off to?', '', 21154),
(110298, 'ruRU', 'Ah, and you are joined by one of the mortals who freed us from the grip of the Old God! We must hold a feast to celebrate!', '', 21154),
(110299, 'ruRU', 'It''ll have to wait, Thorim. There''s a crazed vrykul on her way here with Titanstrike to steal its power!', '', 21154),
(110300, 'ruRU', 'Then we shall slay them together! Come, vrykul! Face the fury of the storms!', '', 21154),
(110301, 'ruRU', '<Suffering from a fever. If you know how to treat a fever, you''ll know how to heal him.>', '<Suffering from a fever. If you know how to treat a fever, you''ll know how to heal her.>', 21154),
(110302, 'ruRU', 'Thanks!', 'Thanks!', 21154),
(110303, 'ruRU', '<Wounded guy on the ground. Heal them up.>', '<Wounded guy on the ground. Heal them up.>', 21154),
(110304, 'ruRU', '<Suffering from a fever. If you know how to treat a fever, you''ll know how to heal him.>', '<Suffering from a fever. If you know how to treat a fever, you''ll know how to heal her.>', 21154),
(110305, 'ruRU', 'Thanks!', 'Thanks!', 21154),
(110306, 'ruRU', 'We''ve done it, I''ll get the piece! The monster''s death has made the area unstable somehow.', '', 21154),
(110307, 'ruRU', 'I''m done! We must hurry, we''ve stirred up the energies here!', '', 21154),
(110308, 'ruRU', 'NO! They are just... gone! You will be remembered.', '', 21154),
(110309, 'ruRU', 'Whew! I thought I was a goner. Thank you!', 'Whew! I thought I was a goner. Thank you!', 21154),
(110310, 'ruRU', 'Our men are down! Help them, I will cover you!', '', 21154),
(110311, 'ruRU', 'Excellent, and no time to waste, let''s move!', '', 21154),
(110312, 'ruRU', 'An intruder! I must warn the others!', '', 21154),
(110313, 'ruRU', 'There you are mortal! I sense you are near, move quickly and head down the path!', '', 21154),
(110314, 'ruRU', 'The master has left and his minions gorge upon my power. Come, introduce them to unfathomable levels of pain for this degradation!', '', 21154),
(110315, 'ruRU', 'Foolish Warlock, did you really think I would remain unaware of your infantile plot to steal my treasure? You underestimate the power of the Nathrezim!', '', 21154),
(110316, 'ruRU', 'As for you, treacherous skull, I''ll deal with you later.', '', 21154),
(110317, 'ruRU', 'Come to me servant of hellfire! Rid me of this uninvited guest.', '', 21154),
(110318, 'ruRU', 'Good! Now, before the master returns, slay my captors and free me!', '', 21154),
(110319, 'ruRU', 'Theodore and I can take ''em! For the wilds!', '', 21154),
(110320, 'ruRU', 'You are quite capable, mage. With their magics gone, I can feel my strength returning.', '', 21154),
(110321, 'ruRU', 'Keep yer eyes peeled! Prustaga''s around here somewhere.', '', 21154),
(110322, 'ruRU', 'Is that the best they can manage? I could do this all day!', '', 21154),
(110323, 'ruRU', 'The Nexus Vault must be weakening, and that arcane energy can only mean Aluneth is no longer fully contained.', '', 21154),
(110324, 'ruRU', '', 'Titanstrike''s power will be mine!', 21154),
(110325, 'ruRU', 'Prust is headed for the throne! We''ve got to stop her!', '', 21154),
(110326, 'ruRU', 'You have great courage to contact me, $r.$b$bOr stupidity...', '', 21154),
(110327, 'ruRU', '', 'Behold my glorious ascension!', 21154),
(110328, 'ruRU', '', 'Yes... I can feel the power of the makers coursing through my veins!', 21154),
(110329, 'ruRU', 'Now what?! One day, I will free myself of your control and... wait... you''re not my master.', '', 21154),
(110330, 'ruRU', 'I have need of your powers.', 'I have need of your powers.', 21154),
(110331, 'ruRU', 'Hah! Do you think you''re the first creature from a doomed world to beg for my aid?$b$bNo, you will burn before the Legion''s power and I''ll continue to suffer in servitude to these mongrels for the rest of eternity.$b$bSave yourself the wasted effort and go jump into a fire!', '', 21154),
(110332, 'ruRU', 'So, the famed Thal''kiel chose to submit to the demons in the end.', 'So, the famed Thal''kiel chose to submit to the demons in the end.', 21154),
(110333, 'ruRU', 'How dare you! If my powers were not constantly being drained I could easily bring them under my control.', '', 21154),
(110334, 'ruRU', 'Then allow me to free you. Together, the Burning Legion will bow to us! We will be the masters!', 'Then allow me to free you. Together, the Burning Legion will bow to us! We will be the masters!', 21154),
(110335, 'ruRU', 'Hmph... fine then. Come to Felsoul Hold if you truly believe you can free me. You better be up for the challenge or you''ll be joining me in eternal torment!', '', 21154),
(110336, 'ruRU', 'The ground is covered with unstable energy. You might not want to step on that...', '', 21154),
(110337, 'ruRU', 'Calydus know where that is! Calydus can help!', '', 21154),
(110338, 'ruRU', '', 'You cannot stop me, fools! I just need... more... power!', 21154),
(110339, 'ruRU', 'It is time we finish this. Hati, kill!', '', 21154),
