(110394, 'ruRU', 'Whew! I thought I was a goner. Thank you!', 'Whew! I thought I was a goner. Thank you!', 21154),
(110395, 'ruRU', '$n! There''s a rumor goin'' round that you''ve got your hands on Felo''melorn. Is it true?', '', 21154),
(110396, 'ruRU', 'Felo''melorn! Last I heard, the Lich King had stowed this beauty in Icecrown. How did you ever recover it?', '', 21154),
(110397, 'ruRU', 'Most of the relics I dig up are inert, but this blade thrums with magical energy. Ohh, it makes me hair stand on end. I hope you know how to use this thing.', '', 21154),
(110398, 'ruRU', 'Thank you, $n. You carry a piece of living history. Treasure it always!', '', 21154),
(110399, 'ruRU', '', 'Are you here to help with our little "problem"?', 21154),
(110400, 'ruRU', '', 'Maldur you ought not to be talkin'' with the Horde. Not after what happened at the Broken Shore.', 21154),
(110401, 'ruRU', 'We tried to mount an expedition into Zarkhenar, but there''s all manner of wrong happening in those ruins.', '', 21154),
(110402, 'ruRU', 'I''ve dug up some relics in my day but nothing like that sword you''ve got there. When that blade was forged, there was no Alliance, no Horde - we dwarves were probably still living in caves. I know it''s a lot to ask, but ... can I hold it?', '', 21154),
(110403, 'ruRU', 'Night falls on the collaborators.', 'Night falls on the collaborators.', 21154),
(110404, 'ruRU', 'Problem? What problem?', 'Problem? What problem?', 21154),
(110405, 'ruRU', 'The nightborne Leodrath seems to have received reinforcements from Suramar. They have reason to believe that the renegade nightfallen have come to Azsuna to escape their grasp.', '', 21154),
(110406, 'ruRU', 'Though they were once my kin, what they have become is an evil that I cannot abide in my lands. You know what you must do.', '', 21154),
(110407, 'ruRU', 'A pity that Leodrath escaped, but you''ve delivered a blow to the Nightborne that they will not soon forget. The denizens of Azsuna thank you.', '', 21154),
(110408, 'ruRU', '', 'Very well. I will prepare a spell that will weaken Thurox significantly, but I''ll need your help to bring him down. Are you ready?', 21154),
(110409, 'ruRU', '', 'Oh, just the shortage of wine in this part of the city! Surely another batch is due soon.', 21154),
