(110448, 'ruRU', 'Use Death Coil on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110449, 'ruRU', 'Oh, that looks like it hurts! After infecting your target with Festering Strike, you are ready to burst the lesions you''ve caused using Scourge Strike! Festering Strike followed by Scourge Strike is a one-two punch few enemies can withstand.', '', 21154),
(110450, 'ruRU', 'When taking excessive damage in battle, Death Strike can help even the odds. Its dark power damages your foe and recovers a portion of your health.', '', 21154),
