(110467, 'ruRU', 'The best way to start a fight as a death knight is to infect your enemy with a host of diseases from a distance. Outbreak will deal damage over time and unleashes a Virulent Plague that spreads to nearby enemies.', '', 21154),
(110468, 'ruRU', 'Your attacks build Runic Power that can be used to cast Death Coil, a spell that hurls a blast of unholy energy at your target and restores energy to your ghoul minion.', '', 21154),
(110469, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As an unholy death knight you command the powers of disease and death. Disease wears your enemy down while your strong melee attacks finish them off. But your greatest ally is death itself. Raise Dead will animate a corpse to serve as your ghoulish minion. You should always try to have a minion with you.', '', 21154),
