(110473, 'ruRU', 'Your minion is dead. Cast Raise Dead to summon a new minion.', '', 21154),
(110474, 'ruRU', 'Using Scourge Strike after Festering Strike is a potent combination!', '', 21154),
(110475, 'ruRU', 'Now that your enemy is reeling from a miasma of plagues, it''s time to strike up close. Festering Strike deals damage and inflicts Festering Wounds on your target.', '', 21154),
