(110500, 'ruRU', 'Use Solar Wrath on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110501, 'ruRU', 'Once your enemy is taking damage from your other attacks, it''s time to unleash Solar Wrath. Solar Wrath is a ranged ability that deals damage and generates Astral Power, a resource used to fuel more powerful attacks.', '', 21154),
(110502, 'ruRU', 'Both these attacks deal damage over time. Once cast, you don''t need to cast them again until their effect on the target has expired.', '', 21154),
(110503, 'ruRU', 'Use Moonfire and Sunfire on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110504, 'ruRU', 'You wield the very power of night and day against your foes. Moonfire and Sunfire represent that power. These attacks deal their damage over time, and either makes an excellent start to a battle.', '', 21154),
(110505, 'ruRU', 'Use Moonkin Form and assume the form of a wildkin.', '', 21154),
(110506, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a balance druid the sun, moon, and stars are your allies, enabling you to unleash these primal powers upon your enemies. You can shapeshift into Moonkin form, which increases both your damage and defense.', '', 21154),
(110507, 'ruRU', 'Use Cat Form.', '', 21154),
(110508, 'ruRU', 'Using spells will usually pull you out of shapeshift forms. Don''t forget to return to cat form for combat.', '', 21154),
