(110510, 'ruRU', 'As a druid you also have the ability to call on the powers of nature for a variety of other abilities, like healing! After you''ve taken damage, use Healing Touch to restore your health.', '', 21154),
(110511, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Dash to increase your movement speed.', '', 21154),
(110512, 'ruRU', 'Ever needed to quickly get out of a sticky situation? Druids excel at doing this. Dash increases your movement speed significantly for a short time. It can''t be used often, so save it for when you really need it.', '', 21154),
