(110536, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a feral druid.', '', 21154),
(110537, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the savagery and cunning of a feral druid!', '', 21154),
(110538, 'ruRU', 'Use Thrash to damage several enemies at once.', '', 21154),
(110539, 'ruRU', 'When fighting multiple enemies at once a feral druid can become a whirlwind of fangs and claws, damaging everything around them. Thrash will damage all nearby enemies, causing them to bleed for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110540, 'ruRU', 'Thrash continues to damage your foes for a short period, so you don''t need to use it again until your targets stops being affected by it.', '', 21154),
(110541, 'ruRU', 'Use Swipe to damage several enemies at once.', '', 21154),
