(110678, 'ruRU', 'Cast Blade of Justice!', '', 21154),
(110679, 'ruRU', 'Blade of Justice is available!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110680, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a retribution paladin.', '', 21154),
(110681, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the courage and zeal of a paladin!', '', 21154),
(110682, 'ruRU', 'Build up Holy Power by using your attacks, then use Templar''s Verdict on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110683, 'ruRU', 'Using Blade of Justice and Crusader Strike in combat builds up Holy Power. Unleash this divine magic through Templar''s Verdict, a powerful melee attack that infuses your weapon with the strength of the Light.', '', 21154),
(110684, 'ruRU', 'Use Crusader Strike on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110685, 'ruRU', 'Blade of Justice is an excellent tool to deal damage as your opponent approaches. Once your foe has closed to striking range, unleash your weapon using Crusader Strike.', '', 21154),
(110686, 'ruRU', 'Use Blade of Justice on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110687, 'ruRU', 'Judgment can be used on enemies at a distance or up close whenever it is available. As your enemy closes in, unleash a potent mid-range attack called Blade of Justice.', '', 21154),
(110688, 'ruRU', 'Use Judgment on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110689, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a retribution paladin you are a stalwart protector of the weak, a bringer of punishment to the unjust! Your attacks are a mix of ranged spells and melee that build up and unleash Holy Power. Your devotion to the Light empowers you to hurl a mighty hammer of Judgment at your foes.', '', 21154),
(110690, 'ruRU', 'Yes, sign me up for the rumble!', 'Yes, sign me up for the rumble!', 21154),
(110691, 'ruRU', 'Use Plea to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110692, 'ruRU', 'You''ve taken damage, but this presents no problem for a priest. The Light gives you the power to restore the health of yourself or your allies.', '', 21154),
(110693, 'ruRU', 'Use Psychic Scream to prevent this group of enemies from hitting you.', '', 21154),
(110694, 'ruRU', 'Well done! In some battles you will face multiple opponents at the same time. Fortunately, you are not defenseless in such cases. Psychic Scream terrifies nearby opponents, causing them to run away in fear.', '', 21154),
(110695, 'ruRU', 'Use Power Word: Shield to prevent taking damage from this enemy.', '', 21154),
(110696, 'ruRU', 'As a priest you have many ways to protect and restore health. One of your most useful defensive abilities is Power Word: Shield, which absorbs all damage from attacks when active. Always remember to maintain your shield during fights.', '', 21154),
(110697, 'ruRU', 'Cast Smite!', '', 21154),
(110698, 'ruRU', 'There''s no need to recast Shadow Word: Pain when the previous one still has lots of time left on it.', '', 21154),
(110699, 'ruRU', 'Cast Shadow Word: Pain!', '', 21154),
(110700, 'ruRU', 'Shadow Word: Pain has expired on your target, cast it again!', '', 21154),
(110701, 'ruRU', 'Use Psychic Scream to cause fear to your enemies!', '', 21154),
(110702, 'ruRU', 'Cast Power Word: Shield to protect yourself!', '', 21154),
(110703, 'ruRU', 'Use Plea to heal yourself!', '', 21154),
(110704, 'ruRU', 'Cast Penance now!', '', 21154),
(110705, 'ruRU', 'Penance is available!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110706, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a discipline priest.', '', 21154),
(110707, 'ruRU', 'Command the forces of Shadow and Light to achieve victory!', '', 21154),
(110708, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadowmend to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110709, 'ruRU', 'Healing can also be provided by the Shadow, but it comes at a cost. Shadowmend is a very powerful heal, but part of that healing will drain away over time.', '', 21154),
(110710, 'ruRU', 'Use Power Word: Barrier to protect these soldiers.', '', 21154),
(110711, 'ruRU', 'You are not limited to only shielding yourself or an ally. A priest can also cast a shield over an entire area, protecting all allies within its boundaries.', '', 21154),
(110712, 'ruRU', 'Use Smite on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110713, 'ruRU', 'The power of the Light allows you to Smite any enemy that stands before you! It is your most frequently used damage spell, best used when Penance is not available.', '', 21154),
(110714, 'ruRU', 'Use Penance on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110715, 'ruRU', 'The Light is a formidable ally, capable of restoring your friends or striking down foes. Penance is a potent spell that deals damage to your enemies. Use Penance whenever it is available.', '', 21154),
(110716, 'ruRU', 'Your target is now afflicted with shadow damage. Use Shadow Word: Pain whenever your target is not already affected by it.', '', 21154),
(110717, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadow Word: Pain on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110718, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Discipline priests draw upon the opposing forces of Light and Shadow, choosing when to heal and when to inflict damage. Shadow Word: Pain taints your foes with shadow energy, wounding them slowly over time.', '', 21154),
(110719, 'ruRU', 'Use Vanish to evade this brute.', '', 21154),
(110720, 'ruRU', 'There''s just one last thing you need to learn. Sometimes a strategic retreat is necessary so you can live to fight another day. Vanish allows you to disengage from combat and make a quick getaway.', '', 21154),
(110721, 'ruRU', 'Shadowstrike to a target, generate 5 combo points with Backstab, and finish them with Eviscerate. That should leave you in stealth, ready to Shadowstrike to your next target.', '', 21154),
(110722, 'ruRU', 'You''re learning how to paint with a dagger. Now it''s time to perfect your art.', '', 21154),
(110723, 'ruRU', 'You''re in trouble! Use Vanish!', '', 21154),
(110724, 'ruRU', 'Use Backstab to generate combo points.', '', 21154),
(110725, 'ruRU', 'Starting combat from stealth is more effective.', '', 21154),
