(110818, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies. Try using Crash Lightning!', '', 21154),
(110819, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as an enhancement shaman.', '', 21154),
(110820, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the fury of the elements as only a shaman can!', '', 21154),
(110821, 'ruRU', 'Use Shamanistic Rage to reduce incoming damage.', '', 21154),
(110822, 'ruRU', 'If you find yourself taking too much punishment in a fight, Shamanistic Rage reduces incoming damage for a short period of time. Try it!', '', 21154),
(110823, 'ruRU', 'Use Crash Lightning to dispatch this group of enemies.', '', 21154),
(110824, 'ruRU', 'If you are fighting multiple enemies, it is time to unleash the full fury of the storm! Crash Lightning deals damage to all targets in front of you. Hitting multiple enemies empowers your weapons, dealing even more damage!', '', 21154),
(110825, 'ruRU', 'Use Stormstrike now!', '', 21154),
(110826, 'ruRU', 'Use Stormstrike on the target dummy after Stormfury triggers.', '', 21154),
(110827, 'ruRU', 'Your most powerful Maelstrom-fueled ability is Stormstrike. This attack costs more resources, but deals more damage as well. Thankfully, your melee attacks have a chance to trigger Stormfury, decreasing the cost. Try to use Stormstrike whenever Stormfury triggers.', '', 21154),
(110828, 'ruRU', 'Use Lava Lash on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110829, 'ruRU', 'Using Rockbiter generates Maelstrom, a resource that powers stronger attacks. Lava Lash uses Maelstrom to charge your off-hand weapon with lava, allowing you to deal a mighty blow.', '', 21154),
(110830, 'ruRU', 'Use Rockbiter on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110831, 'ruRU', 'Now that your weapons are burning, you can focus on your primary attack. Rockbiter empowers your weapons with the forces of earth to deal damage.', '', 21154),
(110832, 'ruRU', 'Use Flametongue on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110833, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As an enhancement shaman you channel the elemental forces directly into your weapons to make yourself a furious melee combatant, beating down your foes with the power of flame, earth, and storm. The first attack we''ll try is Flametongue, which emblazes your weapons and scorches your enemy with fire.', '', 21154),
(110834, 'ruRU', 'Astounding! I knew warlocks had this power, but it''s still impressive to see in action.', '', 21154),
(110835, 'ruRU', 'Use Soulstone to survive death.', '', 21154),
(110836, 'ruRU', 'A well-prepared warlock can survive almost anything... even death! Using your Soulstone ability preserves your very soul for later. Don''t worry, you weren''t using it anyway! With your soul stored, you can return from the dead at will.', '', 21154),
(110837, 'ruRU', 'Now, heal some of the damage you''ve taken with your Healthstone.', '', 21154),
(110838, 'ruRU', 'Now, heal some of the damage you''ve taken with your Healthstone.', '', 21154),
(110839, 'ruRU', 'Use Create Healthstone.', '', 21154),
(110840, 'ruRU', 'A portion of your power can be coalesced into a Healthstone. If you take damage, ingest the Healthstone to recover health.', '', 21154),
(110841, 'ruRU', 'Use Summon Doomguard if you need a boost of damage in a fight!', '', 21154),
(110842, 'ruRU', 'While greater demons like Infernals and Doomguards cannot be controlled for long, you can summon one to your side for short periods of time to fight for you. You cannot do this often, so save this demon for an emergency.', '', 21154),
(110843, 'ruRU', 'Use Fear to frighten this soldier.', '', 21154),
(110844, 'ruRU', 'At times you may find yourself overwhelmed by multiple enemies, or a single enemy that is too strong for you. To force a foe to stop fighting for a short time, utilize fear itself to strike terror into their heart.', '', 21154),
(110845, 'ruRU', 'Use Life Tap to replenish your mana reserves.', '', 21154),
(110846, 'ruRU', 'Many spells have a heavy mana cost. Warlocks have a clever way around this problem. Life Tap allows you to steal your own life force to replenish your mana. Don''t worry, you can always drain the life from your opponent to heal.', '', 21154),
(110847, 'ruRU', 'Use Summon Voidwalker to summon your demonic minion.', '', 21154),
(110848, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Affliction warlocks use shadow magic and disease to wear down their enemies, then drain their very life essences to empower themselves. Your command of dark magic enables you to summon a demon servant to do your bidding.', '', 21154),
(110849, 'ruRU', 'You have maximum Soul Shards. Cast Unstable Affliction!', '', 21154),
(110850, 'ruRU', 'Use Unstable Affliction!', '', 21154),
(110851, 'ruRU', 'Unstable Affliction is available! Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110852, 'ruRU', 'Your Voidwalker has died. Use Summon Voidwalker to bring it back.', '', 21154),
(110853, 'ruRU', 'You''re low on mana. Use Life Tap to replenish it!', '', 21154),
(110854, 'ruRU', 'You''re low on health, use your Healthstone!', '', 21154),
(110855, 'ruRU', 'Now might be a good time to use Fear on your target!', '', 21154),
(110856, 'ruRU', 'Use Drain Life!', '', 21154),
