(110982, 'ruRU', '<The adventurer has broken their leg. If you knew how to set bones, you could treat him.>', '<The adventurer has broken their leg. If you knew how to set bones, you could treat her>', 21154),
(110983, 'ruRU', '<Wounded guy needs help. Heal them up.>', '<Wounded guy needs help. Heal them up.>', 21154),
(110984, 'ruRU', '<The adventurer has broken their leg. If you knew how to set bones, you could treat him.>', '<The adventurer has broken their leg. If you knew how to set bones, you could treat her>', 21154),
(110985, 'ruRU', 'Thanks!', 'Thanks!', 21154),
(110986, 'ruRU', 'Your persistence will be the death of you! Minions, attack!', '', 21154),
(110987, 'ruRU', 'It has been ages since I have seen the Tidestone whole, but there it stands.', '', 21154),
(110988, 'ruRU', 'I and my people owe you a debt of gratitude that we can never repay.', '', 21154),
(110989, 'ruRU', 'Please return to Azsuna as soon as you can. There is much yet left to do, $n.', '', 21154),
(110990, 'ruRU', 'Can you hear me, mortal? Mephistroth has imprisoned me at the far side of the valley. Hurry, I sense he is preparing for something... something big.', '', 21154),
(110991, 'ruRU', 'Enjoy this victory while you can, Warlock. This isn''t over between us; it has only just begun!', '', 21154),
