(111258, 'ruRU', 'Yes, I see.$b$bI''d like you to do something for me, $n. Take this enchanted pen and paper and survey archaeological digsites so that my pen may make notes of your process.$b$bReturn to me when you''re finished and bring me back anything you find.$b$bIf you don''t already know how to survey, just talk to Dariness, I''m sure she can fill you in again on the finer points of being an archaeologist.', '', 21154),
(111259, 'ruRU', 'I remember the night Orgrim fell, run through by a knight''s lance during the liberation of the last orc internment camp. As he bled out onto the fields of Arathi, he bestowed the Doomhammer to me.', '', 21154),
