(111277, 'ruRU', 'During the Cataclysm, I spent many terrible weeks as a prisoner in the Abyssal Maw. I have no desire to return there, but I know the place well.', '', 21154),
(111278, 'ruRU', 'Sharas''dal, the Scepter of Tides, is steeped in Legend. Through its power, Azshara enabled her followers to live in the sea.', '', 21154),
(111279, 'ruRU', '', 'Is it dangerous?', 21154),
(111280, 'ruRU', 'It has dominion of the waters of Azeroth, the very stuff of life. In the right hands, it could be a font of healing instead of corruption.', '', 21154),
(111281, 'ruRU', '', 'This realm belongs to Azshara now, shaman. How fitting that the Earthen Ring will be swept away by the sea!', 21154),
(111282, 'ruRU', '', 'I used to be a great enchanter once, before I fell. Now my spirit is bound to my home.$b$bIf only I could have my enchanting rod back...', 21154),
