(112309, 'ruRU', 'Jabrul loves the stones.$b$bJabrul is happy that you love the stones, too.', '', 21154),
(112310, 'ruRU', '', '$n, is it true you wield the Kingslayers? The very blades that murdered Wrynn during the first war? I would never say this aloud in Stormwind but... he had it coming.', 21154),
(112311, 'ruRU', '', '$n! Master assassin, in the flesh! Those daggers of yours are the talk of Undercity.', 21154),
