(112363, 'ruRU', 'Quiet now. They haven''t found my position yet. I''ve been stirring up a good deal of trouble back here.$b$bMy fellows in the Hall of Shadows report that you''ve got your hands on Garona''s old daggers. Is that true? May I see them?', '', 21154),
(112364, 'ruRU', 'Psst! $n! Come this way. I''m over here. Near the Campfire.', '', 21154),
(112365, 'ruRU', 'So the rumors are true. Anguish and Sorrow are once again in the hands of a skilled assassin. Ah yes, they do not disappoint.', '', 21154),
(112366, 'ruRU', 'Do you see these channels here, along the flat of the blade? They drive poison deeper into the wounds. These blades drink blood and spit poison. Such deadly craftsmanship!', '', 21154),
