(112375, 'ruRU', 'Those daggers you hold. They have tasted the blood of Kings. Give them here, I wish to see them closer.$b$bHah ha! Such a sour face you make. I will not keep them, rogue. I am long past the need for your mortal steel.', '', 21154),
(112376, 'ruRU', 'Come closer, $c. Let me see those blades - they stink of death.', '', 21154),
