(112436, 'ruRU', '<He lifts his head a little to peer at you, expression dubious.>\n\nYou can start with handing over that wine. How dare you tease me like this? You have never gone without! I can see it in your eyes! \n\nDo not insult me with your condescension.', '<She lifts her head a little to peer at you, expression dubious.>\n\nYou can start with handing over that wine. How dare you tease me like this? You have never gone without! I can see it in your eyes! \n\nDo not insult me with your condescension.', 21154),
