(112713, 'ruRU', 'Use Crimson Vial to restore some of your health.', '', 21154),
(112714, 'ruRU', 'A rogue''s reflexes are far superior to those of the average person. In times of extreme danger, a rogue can rely on these catlike reflexes to avoid almost any physical attack for a short time. Evasion can''t be used too often, so save it for emergencies.', '', 21154),
(112715, 'ruRU', 'Use Evasion to increase your chance to dodge incoming attacks.', '', 21154),
